:06.000Z"/><meta itemProp="dateModified" content="2018-06-25T07:18:15.000Z"/><meta itemProp="commentCount" content="204"/><div class="RichContent RichContent--unescapable"><div class="RichContent-inner"><span class="RichText ztext CopyrightRichText-richText" itemProp="text"><p>2018年6月25更新</p><p>由于很多原因很久没更新了，下面的很多游戏现在可能也下架了，趁现在有空决定慢慢写点游戏推荐，欢迎关注，会不定期更新一些好玩的游戏哒~</p><a target="_blank" href="https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/38456960" data-draft-node="block" data-draft-type="link-card" data-image="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-d628d14ca7fd14652a000bbd329a2327_180x120.jpg" data-image-width="2448" data-image-height="983" class="LinkCard LinkCard--hasImage"><span class="LinkCard-backdrop" style="background-image:url(https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-d628d14ca7fd14652a000bbd329a2327_180x120.jpg)"></span><span class="LinkCard-content"><span><span class="LinkCard-title" data-text="true">楚楚：游戏推荐第一发——友尽分手游戏Overcooked</span><span class="LinkCard-meta"><span style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center">​<svg class="Zi Zi--InsertLink" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="17" height="17"><path d="M6.77 17.23c-.905-.904-.94-2.333-.08-3.193l3.059-3.06-1.192-1.19-3.059 3.058c-1.489 1.489-1.427 3.954.138 5.519s4.03 1.627 5.519.138l3.059-3.059-1.192-1.192-3.059 3.06c-.86.86-2.289.824-3.193-.08zm3.016-8.673l1.192 1.192 3.059-3.06c.86-.86 2.289-.824 3.193.08.905.905.94 2.334.08 3.194l-3.059 3.06 1.192 1.19 3.059-3.058c1.489-1.489 1.427-3.954-.138-5.519s-4.03-1.627-5.519-.138L9.786 8.557zm-1.023 6.68c.33.33.863.343 1.177.029l5.34-5.34c.314-.314.3-.846-.03-1.176-.33-.33-.862-.344-1.176-.03l-5.34 5.34c-.314.314-.3.846.03 1.177z" fill-rule="evenodd"></path></svg></span>zhuanlan.zhihu.com</span></span><span class="LinkCard-imageCell"><img class="LinkCard-image LinkCard-image--horizontal" alt="图标" src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-d628d14ca7fd14652a000bbd329a2327_180x120.jpg"/></span></span></a><hr><p>没想到拿了这么多赞，看来喜欢玩解谜游戏的小伙伴很多呀~</p><p>之后也会慢慢推荐自己玩过的不错的游戏的~</p><p>==============我是原文分割线君==============</p><p>安利一些个人觉得比较好玩的游戏吧，由于是女生，而且超爱解谜游戏，所以大部分会是休闲游戏还有解谜游戏~</p><p><b>解谜类</b></p><p><b>1.the room 系列</b></p><p>十分经典的密室逃脱游戏，当时玩的时候还只有英文版的，刚上手可能有点难，但是打开一个个盒子的时候超有成就感，画面和机关做的都很精美。</p><p><b>2.Broken Age 破碎时光</b></p><p>强烈推荐！而且今年刚出了第二章，画面精美，情节很吸引人，第一章最后简直没有想到故事还能这样发展，太有创意了。而且游戏中可以与很多人物进行交流，很有趣，了解到很多游戏背景。</p><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/c34ebbafb05dac593dd3e9d4d86416e3_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="580" data-rawheight="434" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="580" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/c34ebbafb05dac593dd3e9d4d86416e3_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='580'%20height='434'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="580" data-rawheight="434" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="580" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/c34ebbafb05dac593dd3e9d4d86416e3_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic4.zhimg.com/c34ebbafb05dac593dd3e9d4d86416e3_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/0e2e63befa123b1cc2dbdc75948ba02f_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="580" data-rawheight="435" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="580" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/0e2e63befa123b1cc2dbdc75948ba02f_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='580'%20height='435'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="580" data-rawheight="435" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="580" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/0e2e63befa123b1cc2dbdc75948ba02f_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic4.zhimg.com/0e2e63befa123b1cc2dbdc75948ba02f_b.jpg"></figure><p><b>3.The Silent Age 沉默年代</b></p><p>故事情节很有新意，游戏画面很复古，解谜过程中需要不断穿梭过去与未来，最后的结局也很意外。</p><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/b2572ae9f38d7741f43d7ed70952b8e9_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="520" data-rawheight="293" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="520" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/b2572ae9f38d7741f43d7ed70952b8e9_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='520'%20height='293'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="520" data-rawheight="293" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="520" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/b2572ae9f38d7741f43d7ed70952b8e9_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic2.zhimg.com/b2572ae9f38d7741f43d7ed70952b8e9_b.jpg"></figure><p><b>4.纪念碑谷</b></p><p>画面太好看了，而且利用视角错觉来进行游戏，大赞！</p><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/437b36d376b5119a1e97d132169f7c0f_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="300" data-rawheight="417" class="content_image" width="300"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='300'%20height='417'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="300" data-rawheight="417" class="content_image lazy" width="300" data-actualsrc="https://pic4.zhimg.com/437b36d376b5119a1e97d132169f7c0f_b.jpg"></figure><p><b>5.Tengami</b></p><p>整个游戏类似于一个立体书，然后通过滑动翻页等动作来解谜，画面音乐都很美。</p><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/efc5d4c960d60f7b7e8effb0f0954758_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="620" data-rawheight="300" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="620" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/efc5d4c960d60f7b7e8effb0f0954758_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='620'%20height='300'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="620" data-rawheight="300" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="620" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/efc5d4c960d60f7b7e8effb0f0954758_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic1.zhimg.com/efc5d4c960d60f7b7e8effb0f0954758_b.jpg"></figure><p><br></p><p><b>6. Machinarium 机械迷城</b></p><p>很经典的解谜游戏了，画面很精致，但是谜题难度有点大。</p><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/0f3ee73de10277d82056ed66ab219be3_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="1280" data-rawheight="800" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1280" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/0f3ee73de10277d82056ed66ab219be3_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1280'%20height='800'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="1280" data-rawheight="800" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="1280" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/0f3ee73de10277d82056ed66ab219be3_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic4.zhimg.com/0f3ee73de10277d82056ed66ab219be3_b.jpg"></figure><p><b>7.Botanicula 植物精灵</b></p><p>也是机械迷城开发商的作品，画面很美，操控一群小植物来拯救森林，配音炒鸡萌，解谜略有点难度。</p><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/7782b7be23acc8df6d3991f7864bdc93_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="500" data-rawheight="281" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="500" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/7782b7be23acc8df6d3991f7864bdc93_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='500'%20height='281'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="500" data-rawheight="281" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="500" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/7782b7be23acc8df6d3991f7864bdc93_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic4.zhimg.com/7782b7be23acc8df6d3991f7864bdc93_b.jpg"></figure><p><br></p><p>这是游戏里的地图，很有特色。</p><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/a4f6dffad6c191ddb2e635d360977371_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="500" data-rawheight="294" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="500" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/a4f6dffad6c191ddb2e635d360977371_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='500'%20height='294'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="500" data-rawheight="294" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="500" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/a4f6dffad6c191ddb2e635d360977371_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic2.zhimg.com/a4f6dffad6c191ddb2e635d360977371_b.jpg"></figure><p><b>8.Limbo地狱边境</b></p><p>画面全是黑白，游戏过程中会死很多次，始终记得最后那只大蜘蛛死的时候把腿一根根拔下来，还是略有些诡异，游戏还是挺好玩的。</p><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/16b56e81faf0463394d1e2ec880b0dca_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="700" data-rawheight="394" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="700" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/16b56e81faf0463394d1e2ec880b0dca_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='700'%20height='394'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="700" data-rawheight="394" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="700" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/16b56e81faf0463394d1e2ec880b0dca_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic3.zhimg.com/16b56e81faf0463394d1e2ec880b0dca_b.jpg"></figure><p><b>9.Tiny Thief</b></p><p>游戏画风很可爱，很幽默，有些关卡还是挺难的。</p><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/76c2c30b5e2ab621ddabd60304c55429_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="480" data-rawheight="360" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="480" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/76c2c30b5e2ab621ddabd60304c55429_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='480'%20height='360'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="480" data-rawheight="360" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="480" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/76c2c30b5e2ab621ddabd60304c55429_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic2.zhimg.com/76c2c30b5e2ab621ddabd60304c55429_b.jpg"></figure><p><br></p><p><b>10.Hamlet！</b></p><p>也是点击式的解谜游戏，画风可爱，游戏谜题设计很有创意。</p><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/7b29326051313b0fc01a9ad15a187b0d_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="580" data-rawheight="435" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="580" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/7b29326051313b0fc01a9ad15a187b0d_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='580'%20height='435'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="580" data-rawheight="435" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="580" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/7b29326051313b0fc01a9ad15a187b0d_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic2.zhimg.com/7b29326051313b0fc01a9ad15a187b0d_b.jpg"></figure><p><br></p><p>下面是比较传统的解谜类游戏，选了几个自己认为比较有特色的</p><p><b>1.迷画之塔系列 （貌似目前ios已经下架了，想玩的同学应该还是能找到PC资源的）</b></p><p>共有3部，分别是Drawn: The Painted Tower，Drawn: Dark Flight，Drawn: Trail of Shadows</p><p>画面很漂亮，情节设置很新颖的是需要进入很多画中去解谜，上几张图就知道有多美了。</p><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/0605df11d121dc30d5f43f79da443486_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="2048" data-rawheight="1536" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="2048" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/0605df11d121dc30d5f43f79da443486_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='2048'%20height='1536'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="2048" data-rawheight="1536" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="2048" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/0605df11d121dc30d5f43f79da443486_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic3.zhimg.com/0605df11d121dc30d5f43f79da443486_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/ca6f4ee956ca1f5c7f417c8c6176511a_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="2048" data-rawheight="1536" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="2048" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/ca6f4ee956ca1f5c7f417c8c6176511a_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='2048'%20height='1536'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="2048" data-rawheight="1536" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="2048" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/ca6f4ee956ca1f5c7f417c8c6176511a_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic3.zhimg.com/ca6f4ee956ca1f5c7f417c8c6176511a_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/f01998c588c92560662f862f073d68ff_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="690" data-rawheight="431" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="690" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/f01998c588c92560662f862f073d68ff_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='690'%20height='431'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="690" data-rawheight="431" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="690" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/f01998c588c92560662f862f073d68ff_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic4.zhimg.com/f01998c588c92560662f862f073d68ff_b.jpg"></figure><p><b>2.黑暗寓言Dark Parables系列 </b></p><p>目前ios上有7部，个人比较推荐第三部冰雪女王的崛起和第四部小红帽骑士团，这个系列都是改编自我们熟悉的童话故事，画面也是相当的漂亮（原谅我是颜控），而且没有单词找物，谜题机关也有一定难度。</p><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/876369f92b790db7c9933b1fd0f4e045_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="580" data-rawheight="435" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="580" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/876369f92b790db7c9933b1fd0f4e045_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='580'%20height='435'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="580" data-rawheight="435" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="580" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/876369f92b790db7c9933b1fd0f4e045_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic2.zhimg.com/876369f92b790db7c9933b1fd0f4e045_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/cd3905775c12b05572bf7fefc265091e_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="580" data-rawheight="435" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="580" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/cd3905775c12b05572bf7fefc265091e_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='580'%20height='435'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="580" data-rawheight="435" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="580" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/cd3905775c12b05572bf7fefc265091e_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic3.zhimg.com/cd3905775c12b05572bf7fefc265091e_b.jpg"></figure><p><b>3.Special Enquiry Detail系列</b></p><p>ios上出了2部，都很不错，故事很完整，有一种自己在破案的感觉，画面精致，特别是找到证据回来化验的部分很逼真。</p><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/9c031ac71600cff39d6885777b3ca2c2_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="512" data-rawheight="320" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="512" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/9c031ac71600cff39d6885777b3ca2c2_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='512'%20height='320'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="512" data-rawheight="320" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="512" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/9c031ac71600cff39d6885777b3ca2c2_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic3.zhimg.com/9c031ac71600cff39d6885777b3ca2c2_b.jpg"></figure><p><b>4. Enigmatis系列</b></p><p>出了2部，侦探类解谜游戏，小游戏可玩性很强，画面好看，很特别的是所有找到的证据都会被贴在一个墙上，然后需要我们将不同的证据去归类推理。</p><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/b77d757a088d932b0dbf3713735095e6_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="580" data-rawheight="435" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="580" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/b77d757a088d932b0dbf3713735095e6_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='580'%20height='435'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="580" data-rawheight="435" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="580" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/b77d757a088d932b0dbf3713735095e6_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic3.zhimg.com/b77d757a088d932b0dbf3713735095e6_b.jpg"></figure><p><b>5.Royal Trouble</b></p><p>这个解谜游戏情节十分搞笑有趣，而且在游戏过程中需要分别控制男女主人公去完成任务。</p><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/9f95396943364e4ae74803078a5d1a03_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="760" data-rawheight="383" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="760" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/9f95396943364e4ae74803078a5d1a03_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='760'%20height='383'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="760" data-rawheight="383" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="760" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/9f95396943364e4ae74803078a5d1a03_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic4.zhimg.com/9f95396943364e4ae74803078a5d1a03_b.jpg"></figure><p><b>6.被错过的天堂</b></p><p>这款游戏画风略诡异，但是最终的结局很意外，而且有两个结局，情节上还是值得玩一玩的。</p><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/0d1192474229ca659c15493ae1d95723_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="500" data-rawheight="290" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="500" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/0d1192474229ca659c15493ae1d95723_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='500'%20height='290'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="500" data-rawheight="290" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="500" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/0d1192474229ca659c15493ae1d95723_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic4.zhimg.com/0d1192474229ca659c15493ae1d95723_b.jpg"></figure><p><br></p><p><b>消除类</b></p><p><b>1.宝石迷阵</b></p><p>消除类鼻祖不解释。</p><p><b>2.candy crush系列</b></p><p>关卡很多，而且今年新出的soda里的小熊简直太萌了有木有，缺点就是玩到后面关卡太难了，体力不够。</p><p><b>3.蒙特祖玛的宝藏系列</b></p><p>游戏画面很精美，而且有剧情，还有小游戏，新出的第四部还有很多种游戏模式。</p><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/092c071af6e44d818d5787f653149a0a_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="1280" data-rawheight="720" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1280" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/092c071af6e44d818d5787f653149a0a_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1280'%20height='720'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="1280" data-rawheight="720" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="1280" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/092c071af6e44d818d5787f653149a0a_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic3.zhimg.com/092c071af6e44d818d5787f653149a0a_b.jpg"></figure><p><b>4.亚特兰蒂斯系列</b></p><p>Playrix家的游戏，他们家的消除游戏都很好玩，现在有3部，我玩过Call of Atlantis，关卡很多，消磨时间很不错。</p><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/b23a9f4090fc822a76caf2b29d8b2e94_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="480" data-rawheight="320" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="480" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/b23a9f4090fc822a76caf2b29d8b2e94_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='480'%20height='320'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="480" data-rawheight="320" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="480" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/b23a9f4090fc822a76caf2b29d8b2e94_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic1.zhimg.com/b23a9f4090fc822a76caf2b29d8b2e94_b.jpg"></figure><p><b>5.4 Elements系列</b></p><p>也是Playrix出的，共有2部，划线类消除，需要通过消除联通起点到终点。</p><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/f003ad69c29a6357dee41db361b4e043_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="480" data-rawheight="360" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="480" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/f003ad69c29a6357dee41db361b4e043_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='480'%20height='360'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="480" data-rawheight="360" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="480" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/f003ad69c29a6357dee41db361b4e043_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic4.zhimg.com/f003ad69c29a6357dee41db361b4e043_b.jpg"></figure><p><b>6.Puzzle Craft</b></p><p>强烈推荐的一款划线类消除，结合了经营游戏的特点，划线消除的物品可以升级，最后玩家可以将小镇子升级成城堡。</p><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/a9a4ba969ba075dd9010f6252405453c_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="400" data-rawheight="533" class="content_image" width="400"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='400'%20height='533'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="400" data-rawheight="533" class="content_image lazy" width="400" data-actualsrc="https://pic1.zhimg.com/a9a4ba969ba075dd9010f6252405453c_b.jpg"></figure><p><b>7. Puzzle to the Center of the Earth</b></p><p>也是划线消除，结合了冒险解谜，需要带领矿工通过消除一步步深入地下，并打开机关宝藏，关卡越往后越难，到现在我都还没全部通关……</p><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/2bd55a1eddbf9a31634fe8213c2f27eb_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="360" data-rawheight="640" class="content_image" width="360"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='360'%20height='640'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="360" data-rawheight="640" class="content_image lazy" width="360" data-actualsrc="https://pic4.zhimg.com/2bd55a1eddbf9a31634fe8213c2f27eb_b.jpg"></figure><p><br></p><p><b>模拟经营类</b></p><p><b>1.美味餐厅Delicious系列</b></p><p>ios上出了7部，几乎每部都玩过，很耐玩，而且除了卖食物以外还有其他的任务，剧情也很棒！</p><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/a8b3a9fe435cd7a5681c0166efa3e4fe_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="600" data-rawheight="449" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="600" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/a8b3a9fe435cd7a5681c0166efa3e4fe_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='600'%20height='449'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="600" data-rawheight="449" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="600" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/a8b3a9fe435cd7a5681c0166efa3e4fe_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic3.zhimg.com/a8b3a9fe435cd7a5681c0166efa3e4fe_b.jpg"></figure><p><b>2.卡通农场 Hay Day</b></p><p>去年很火的一款农场经营游戏，卡通画风，画面很精致，而且作为经营类游戏从植物种植到加工到卖出去都很考验玩家经营策略，截一张我自己的农场图吧。</p><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/3bac5b868901b20ee6c6cd94b17ea81b_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="1334" data-rawheight="750" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1334" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/3bac5b868901b20ee6c6cd94b17ea81b_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1334'%20height='750'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="1334" data-rawheight="750" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="1334" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/3bac5b868901b20ee6c6cd94b17ea81b_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic4.zhimg.com/3bac5b868901b20ee6c6cd94b17ea81b_b.jpg"></figure><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><b>塔防类</b><br><b>1.保卫萝卜</b><br>风格很萌，而且也不算太难，女生应该都喜欢吧。<br><b>2.Kingdom Rush</b><br>本就人气很高的塔防游戏，塔防类型很丰富，升级还有不同的分支，还有英雄养成系统。<br>估计大家对这两个游戏都很熟悉就不截图了。</p><p><b>其他</b></p><p>不知道怎么分类了，就按自己玩的顺序来推荐吧~</p><p><b>1.Shoot The Zombirds</b></p><p>射击动作类游戏，画面有点阴森，但是一旦开始玩就会欲罢不能！</p><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/9653ca1afea14427f50f1d3fbaf86149_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="480" data-rawheight="320" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="480" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/9653ca1afea14427f50f1d3fbaf86149_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='480'%20height='320'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="480" data-rawheight="320" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="480" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/9653ca1afea14427f50f1d3fbaf86149_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic2.zhimg.com/9653ca1afea14427f50f1d3fbaf86149_b.jpg"></figure><p><b>2.鳄鱼小顽皮爱洗澡系列</b></p><p>Disney出品的益智类游戏，同类的还有一个米奇小顽皮和鸭嘴兽泰瑞，通过挖开土引导水流让小顽皮成功洗澡，关卡很多而且有些难度还挺大。</p><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/6beb7fbe917de6d69c54655c4659fbc5_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="491" data-rawheight="357" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="491" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/6beb7fbe917de6d69c54655c4659fbc5_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='491'%20height='357'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="491" data-rawheight="357" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="491" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/6beb7fbe917de6d69c54655c4659fbc5_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic2.zhimg.com/6beb7fbe917de6d69c54655c4659fbc5_b.jpg"></figure><p><b>3.TripleTown 三重镇</b></p><p>火过一时的益智游戏，利用相同的物品合体成高级物品，游戏风格也很可爱，比较耐玩。</p><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/7344f085d37cdd83c4b7e93f16279d3f_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="600" data-rawheight="444" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="600" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/7344f085d37cdd83c4b7e93f16279d3f_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='600'%20height='444'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="600" data-rawheight="444" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="600" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/7344f085d37cdd83c4b7e93f16279d3f_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic4.zhimg.com/7344f085d37cdd83c4b7e93f16279d3f_b.jpg"></figure><p><b>4.Puzzle Forge2</b></p><p>最近正在玩，跟三重镇很像，也是合成各种兵器，但是可以给兵器附魔加宝石，而且每一关都有任务，过关后还能升级，耐玩度更高了。</p><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/c948deec52a1a2a166d3fcf2fd0fbf0a_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="750" data-rawheight="1334" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="750" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/c948deec52a1a2a166d3fcf2fd0fbf0a_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='750'%20height='1334'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="750" data-rawheight="1334" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="750" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/c948deec52a1a2a166d3fcf2fd0fbf0a_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic3.zhimg.com/c948deec52a1a2a166d3fcf2fd0fbf0a_b.jpg"></figure><p><b>5. Find the Line</b></p><p>看之前有人推荐了Blueprint 3D，这款游戏是平面的线条拼图，需要玩家将各组线条找到合适的位置拼成一幅图，很有创意，上个视频就知道了。</p><a class="video-box" href="https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//v.youku.com/v_show/id_XNzE1OTkzNjYw.html" target="_blank" data-video-id="" data-video-playable="false" data-name="休闲益智解谜手游《彩线拼图》预告片—在线播放—优酷网，视频高清在线观看" data-poster="http://r3.ykimg.com/05420408537F26C46A0A42506729EE45" data-lens-id="">              <img class="thumbnail" src="http://r3.ykimg.com/05420408537F26C46A0A42506729EE45">              <span class="content">                <span class="title">休闲益智解谜手游《彩线拼图》预告片—在线播放—优酷网，视频高清在线观看<span class="z-ico-extern-gray"></span><span class="z-ico-extern-blue"></span></span>                <span class="url"><span class="z-ico-video"></span>http://v.youku.com/v_show/id_XNzE1OTkzNjYw.html</span>              </span>            </a>            <p><b> 6. 疯狂填字系列</b></p><p>填字游戏，跟朋友家人一起玩感觉很好！而且关卡多，绝对耐玩。</p><p><b>7.小东西长久远</b></p><p>找物游戏，画面很可爱，就是有点伤眼睛。</p><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/b118dac158eb065dd28dd56d8ab6f5b2_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="520" data-rawheight="292" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="520" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/b118dac158eb065dd28dd56d8ab6f5b2_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='520'%20height='292'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="520" data-rawheight="292" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="520" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/b118dac158eb065dd28dd56d8ab6f5b2_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic3.zhimg.com/b118dac158eb065dd28dd56d8ab6f5b2_b.jpg"></figure><p><b>8.Numerity</b></p><p>也是找物，在一群数字中找出特定的数字，最后会组成一幅画，挺有创意的。</p><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/7713834c23e44c23cfac9bebf0a0bbad_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="568" data-rawheight="419" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="568" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/7713834c23e44c23cfac9bebf0a0bbad_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='568'%20height='419'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="568" data-rawheight="419" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="568" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/7713834c23e44c23cfac9bebf0a0bbad_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic2.zhimg.com/7713834c23e44c23cfac9bebf0a0bbad_b.jpg"></figure><p><br></p><p>推荐几款适合短时间，比如上厕所或者坐地铁的时候适合玩的小游戏吧~</p><p><b>9.Threes！</b></p><p>想必大家挺熟悉的，游戏就是通过滑动屏幕上的数字来组合成3以及其3的倍数，得到的数字越大分数越高，要拿高分还是有一定规律的，截一个我自己的最高分。</p><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/8bacae65a5990fdf4edea2462b78b7a4_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="750" data-rawheight="1334" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="750" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/8bacae65a5990fdf4edea2462b78b7a4_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='750'%20height='1334'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="750" data-rawheight="1334" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="750" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/8bacae65a5990fdf4edea2462b78b7a4_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic1.zhimg.com/8bacae65a5990fdf4edea2462b78b7a4_b.jpg"></figure><p><b>10.2048</b></p><p>和threes一样，不过改成了2的倍数，难度也降低了，只要将最大的数字放在一个角落就行了。</p><p><b>11. 1010！</b></p><p>俄罗斯方块式的消除游戏，简单但是会上瘾。。。。</p><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/2ef8cdb6c43a80755f49a728fb5007dd_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="750" data-rawheight="1334" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="750" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/2ef8cdb6c43a80755f49a728fb5007dd_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='750'%20height='1334'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="750" data-rawheight="1334" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="750" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/2ef8cdb6c43a80755f49a728fb5007dd_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic2.zhimg.com/2ef8cdb6c43a80755f49a728fb5007dd_b.jpg"></figure><p><b>12. Poptile</b></p><p>点击相同颜色色块的消除游戏，画面简单但是很舒服，也是会上瘾的。</p><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/5cdf642ba356c2e88ce5b37e8dc09e6e_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="750" data-rawheight="1334" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="750" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/5cdf642ba356c2e88ce5b37e8dc09e6e_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='750'%20height='1334'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="750" data-rawheight="1334" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="750" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/5cdf642ba356c2e88ce5b37e8dc09e6e_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic3.zhimg.com/5cdf642ba356c2e88ce5b37e8dc09e6e_b.jpg"></figure><p><b>13.Infinite Loop ∞再环</b></p><p>点击游戏里的半圆全部连起来，类似于连水管的那种游戏，画面很简约，非常消磨时间，已经玩到了快400关，不知道一共有多少关。。。</p><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/c3a7118433c23315f9551c6503c20a27_b.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="750" data-rawheight="1334" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="750" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/c3a7118433c23315f9551c6503c20a27_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='750'%20height='1334'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="750" data-rawheight="1334" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="750" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/c3a7118433c23315f9551c6503c20a27_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic4.zhimg.com/c3a7118433c23315f9551c6503c20a27_b.jpg"></figure></span></div><div><div class="ContentItem-time"><a target="_blank" href="/question/22586211/answer/60617170"><span data-tooltip="发布于 2015-08-24 18:26">编辑于 2018-06-25</span></a></div></div><div class="ContentItem-actions RichContent-actions"><span><button aria-label="赞同" type="button" class="Button VoteButton VoteButton--up"><span style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center">​<svg class="Zi Zi--TriangleUp VoteButton-TriangleUp" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="10" height="10"><path d="M2 18.242c0-.326.088-.532.237-.896l7.98-13.203C10.572 3.57 11.086 3 12 3c.915 0 1.429.571 1.784 1.143l7.98 13.203c.15.364.236.57.236.896 0 1.386-.875 1.9-1.955 1.9H3.955c-1.08 0-1.955-.517-1.955-1.9z" fill-rule="evenodd"></path></svg></span>赞同 <!-- -->4.8K</button><button aria-label="反对" type="button" class="Button VoteButton VoteButton--down"><span style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center">​<svg class="Zi Zi--TriangleDown" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="10" height="10"><path d="M20.044 3H3.956C2.876 3 2 3.517 2 4.9