dd"></path></svg></span>收藏</button><button type="button" class="Button ContentItem-action Button--plain Button--withIcon Button--withLabel"><span style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center">​<svg class="Zi Zi--Heart Button-zi" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="1.2em" height="1.2em"><path d="M2 8.437C2 5.505 4.294 3.094 7.207 3 9.243 3 11.092 4.19 12 6c.823-1.758 2.649-3 4.651-3C19.545 3 22 5.507 22 8.432 22 16.24 13.842 21 12 21 10.158 21 2 16.24 2 8.437z" fill-rule="evenodd"></path></svg></span>感谢</button><button data-zop-retract-question="true" type="button" class="Button ContentItem-action ContentItem-rightButton Button--plain"><span class="RichContent-collapsedText">收起</span><span style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center">​<svg class="Zi Zi--ArrowDown ContentItem-arrowIcon is-active" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24" height="24"><path d="M12 13L8.285 9.218a.758.758 0 0 0-1.064 0 .738.738 0 0 0 0 1.052l4.249 4.512a.758.758 0 0 0 1.064 0l4.246-4.512a.738.738 0 0 0 0-1.052.757.757 0 0 0-1.063 0L12.002 13z" fill-rule="evenodd"></path></svg></span></button></div></div></div></div><div class="List-item"><div class="ContentItem AnswerItem" data-za-index="1" data-zop="{&quot;authorName&quot;:&quot;知乎用户&quot;,&quot;itemId&quot;:259321571,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;有哪些好玩且耐玩的 iOS 游戏？&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;answer&quot;}" name="259321571" itemProp="suggestedAnswer" itemType="http://schema.org/Answer" itemscope=""><div class="ContentItem-meta"><div class="AuthorInfo AnswerItem-authorInfo AnswerItem-authorInfo--related" itemProp="author" itemscope="" itemType="http://schema.org/Person"><meta itemProp="name" content="知乎用户"/><meta itemProp="image" content="https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg"/><meta itemProp="url" content="https://www.zhihu.com/people/"/><meta itemProp="zhihu:followerCount" content="218"/><span class="UserLink AuthorInfo-avatarWrapper"><img class="Avatar AuthorInfo-avatar" width="38" height="38" src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_xs.jpg" srcSet="https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_l.jpg 2x" alt="知乎用户"/></span><div class="AuthorInfo-content"><div class="AuthorInfo-head"><span class="UserLink AuthorInfo-name">知乎用户</span></div><div class="AuthorInfo-detail"><div class="AuthorInfo-badge"></div></div></div></div><div class="AnswerItem-extraInfo"><span class="Voters"><button type="button" class="Button Button--plain">1,550 人<!-- -->赞同了该回答</button></span></div></div><meta itemProp="image" content="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-07a42a87da8141d5aeb2b7323d61f0c7_200x112.jpg"/><meta itemProp="upvoteCount" content="1550"/><meta itemProp="url" content="https://www.zhihu.com/question/22586211/answer/259321571"/><meta itemProp="dateCreated" content="2017-11-13T12:04:09.000Z"/><meta itemProp="dateModified" content="2018-08-10T11:32:57.000Z"/><meta itemProp="commentCount" content="127"/><div class="RichContent RichContent--unescapable"><div class="RichContent-inner"><span class="RichText ztext CopyrightRichText-richText" itemProp="text"><p>看着王者农药不断蚕食着游戏爱好者的宝贵时间，我终于忍不住要在今天祭出我的终极回答来拯(pian)救(ge)你(zan)了！</p><p>呕心沥血整理了40多款游戏，可谓男女通吃，老少皆宜。精心标注游戏分类，游戏时长，让你在高铁，地铁，公交，马桶上不再猥琐发育，随时都能掏出合适的游戏玩耍。对你有帮助的话麻烦点个赞啊。</p><p><br></p><p><b>【角色扮演】</b></p><p>1.魔女之泉系列: Witch Spring（适合30分钟以上游戏时间）</p><p>游戏采用了可爱的3D画风，呆萌的人设和清新的画面令人眼前一亮。无论剧情、画面音乐都十分优秀。冒险中成长的那种酣畅淋漓的紧迫感，令“春巫”系列达到了手机RPG游戏的一种极致的高度。</p><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-07a42a87da8141d5aeb2b7323d61f0c7_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="493" data-rawheight="279" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="493" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-07a42a87da8141d5aeb2b7323d61f0c7_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='493'%20height='279'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="493" data-rawheight="279" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="493" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-07a42a87da8141d5aeb2b7323d61f0c7_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-07a42a87da8141d5aeb2b7323d61f0c7_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-6fffb1903b6e8d04fdad25a21b26e0f0_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="1320" data-rawheight="743" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1320" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-6fffb1903b6e8d04fdad25a21b26e0f0_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1320'%20height='743'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="1320" data-rawheight="743" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="1320" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-6fffb1903b6e8d04fdad25a21b26e0f0_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-6fffb1903b6e8d04fdad25a21b26e0f0_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-d14aad494f07a2bfd08bb6bc1d518ddf_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="1320" data-rawheight="743" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1320" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-d14aad494f07a2bfd08bb6bc1d518ddf_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1320'%20height='743'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="1320" data-rawheight="743" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="1320" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-d14aad494f07a2bfd08bb6bc1d518ddf_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-d14aad494f07a2bfd08bb6bc1d518ddf_b.jpg"></figure><p><br></p><p>2.我在7年后等着你（适合10分钟以上游戏时间）</p><p>游戏的主角是一位失去记忆少年，不断找寻记忆只为了7年前的一个约定。说它是个游戏，但它更像一本书，你只需要点击屏幕来进行对话，但游戏剧情高潮迭起，结局感人至深，令人回味无穷。这就是为什么它能够在taptap获得9.9分的原因吧。</p><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-850c8b2af44500cd5a9da08f444c695c_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="900" data-rawheight="500" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="900" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-850c8b2af44500cd5a9da08f444c695c_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='900'%20height='500'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="900" data-rawheight="500" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="900" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-850c8b2af44500cd5a9da08f444c695c_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-850c8b2af44500cd5a9da08f444c695c_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-2f59e317ba7c14b44b4baf4898017222_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="900" data-rawheight="506" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="900" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-2f59e317ba7c14b44b4baf4898017222_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='900'%20height='506'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="900" data-rawheight="506" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="900" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-2f59e317ba7c14b44b4baf4898017222_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-2f59e317ba7c14b44b4baf4898017222_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-d75b8c6c1e2a41e47a3dedb9913cbccb_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="900" data-rawheight="506" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="900" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-d75b8c6c1e2a41e47a3dedb9913cbccb_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='900'%20height='506'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="900" data-rawheight="506" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="900" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-d75b8c6c1e2a41e47a3dedb9913cbccb_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-d75b8c6c1e2a41e47a3dedb9913cbccb_b.jpg"></figure><p><br></p><p>3.晶体管: Transistor（适合20分钟以上游戏时间）</p><p>一代游戏神作，移植到移动平台，并自带中文，诚意满满。加之超高的游戏品质，获得了好评无数。游戏画面精致，bgm动听，战斗方式新颖酷炫，酣畅淋漓，可以选择即时战斗或者为游戏角色提前预设战斗行动，好玩到停不下来。</p><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-450aebc0600137931d6cc2e89ec327dd_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="900" data-rawheight="506" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="900" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-450aebc0600137931d6cc2e89ec327dd_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='900'%20height='506'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="900" data-rawheight="506" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="900" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-450aebc0600137931d6cc2e89ec327dd_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-450aebc0600137931d6cc2e89ec327dd_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-23f5e959c68bf90bb46e1bc4e727b58e_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="900" data-rawheight="506" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="900" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-23f5e959c68bf90bb46e1bc4e727b58e_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='900'%20height='506'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="900" data-rawheight="506" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="900" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-23f5e959c68bf90bb46e1bc4e727b58e_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-23f5e959c68bf90bb46e1bc4e727b58e_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-14741dc357342945eb27fa7ba2795e57_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="900" data-rawheight="506" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="900" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-14741dc357342945eb27fa7ba2795e57_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='900'%20height='506'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="900" data-rawheight="506" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="900" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-14741dc357342945eb27fa7ba2795e57_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-14741dc357342945eb27fa7ba2795e57_b.jpg"></figure><p><br></p><p>4. 海之号角: oceanhorn（适合20分钟以上游戏时间）</p><p>很像塞尔达的一款手游，虽然赶不上塞尔达这样的神作。它作为一款手游的游戏品质也算的上相当优秀。画面和音乐都十分出色，在主角冒险打怪的过程中出现的谜题也为游戏增添了不少色彩，值得一试。</p><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-242f0851cc867238956298b46d454956_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="1542" data-rawheight="857" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1542" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-242f0851cc867238956298b46d454956_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1542'%20height='857'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="1542" data-rawheight="857" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="1542" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-242f0851cc867238956298b46d454956_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-242f0851cc867238956298b46d454956_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-37bdf5e10c7367952c657ec4f62910a1_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="600" data-rawheight="320" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="600" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-37bdf5e10c7367952c657ec4f62910a1_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='600'%20height='320'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="600" data-rawheight="320" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="600" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-37bdf5e10c7367952c657ec4f62910a1_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-37bdf5e10c7367952c657ec4f62910a1_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-f79a18b4c951a56fed9e6d14ce756627_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="1136" data-rawheight="640" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1136" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-f79a18b4c951a56fed9e6d14ce756627_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1136'%20height='640'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="1136" data-rawheight="640" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="1136" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-f79a18b4c951a56fed9e6d14ce756627_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-f79a18b4c951a56fed9e6d14ce756627_b.jpg"></figure><p><br></p><p>5. 生命线系列: lifeline（任何时间）</p><p>这款游戏是一款文字冒险类游戏啦，但是很带感啊，像和真人对话。玩家需要通过实时通讯的方式给游戏主角指引，帮助游戏主角逃出困境。这种实时通讯的方式，很像有人通过微信和你聊天，给玩家制造了游戏的真实感，会感觉游戏那头的有一个真实的人存在。</p><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-420524304d85f0d6ef69609a90fe5c1b_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="640" data-rawheight="360" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="640" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-420524304d85f0d6ef69609a90fe5c1b_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='640'%20height='360'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="640" data-rawheight="360" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="640" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-420524304d85f0d6ef69609a90fe5c1b_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-420524304d85f0d6ef69609a90fe5c1b_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-6ae4b2703f6dda94c161632fde76e050_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="600" data-rawheight="531" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="600" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-6ae4b2703f6dda94c161632fde76e050_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='600'%20height='531'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="600" data-rawheight="531" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="600" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-6ae4b2703f6dda94c161632fde76e050_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-6ae4b2703f6dda94c161632fde76e050_b.jpg"></figure><p><br></p><p>6. 笨拙忍者:clumsy ninja(适合5分钟以上游戏时间）</p><p>这个其实算养成类游戏吧，但是我没有养成这个分类，所以丢在这里啦。养一个忍者，培养他成为上忍，听着就很酷。但这个忍者的一举一动都暴露了他的呆萌举动，有这么一个忍者，你给我鸣人也不换。游戏画面十分精致，忍者的动作逼真流畅，来领养一个呆萌的忍者吧。</p><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-7c9b357f63dd277876e9918b0dc71c4f_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="501" data-rawheight="398" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="501" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-7c9b357f63dd277876e9918b0dc71c4f_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='501'%20height='398'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="501" data-rawheight="398" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="501" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-7c9b357f63dd277876e9918b0dc71c4f_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-7c9b357f63dd277876e9918b0dc71c4f_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-a7523efdc94fad961de16c1913e2ad35_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="450" data-rawheight="280" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="450" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-a7523efdc94fad961de16c1913e2ad35_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='450'%20height='280'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="450" data-rawheight="280" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="450" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-a7523efdc94fad961de16c1913e2ad35_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-a7523efdc94fad961de16c1913e2ad35_b.jpg"></figure><p><br></p><p><b>【休闲益智】</b></p><p><br></p><p>1. 一起来陶艺：Let’s Create！ Pottery（有5分钟就能玩）</p><p>想要体验制作陶器的乐趣却苦于没有合适的场所，这款游戏就能满足你的需求而且不会弄脏你的双手。玩家需要捏制出于图片相符的陶器来通过关卡，游戏画面精致逼真，让玩家能够真正体会到制陶的乐趣。</p><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-6878ee5675fd5a095f327d75252a1b69_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="705" data-rawheight="344" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="705" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-6878ee5675fd5a095f327d75252a1b69_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='705'%20height='344'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="705" data-rawheight="344" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="705" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-6878ee5675fd5a095f327d75252a1b69_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-6878ee5675fd5a095f327d75252a1b69_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-26c708adbcd6a760b0e9a092e36b86ff_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="550" data-rawheight="450" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="550" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-26c708adbcd6a760b0e9a092e36b86ff_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='550'%20height='450'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="550" data-rawheight="450" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="550" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-26c708adbcd6a760b0e9a092e36b86ff_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-26c708adbcd6a760b0e9a092e36b86ff_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-5b013417dff3db79bf706e58fac23f62_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="550" data-rawheight="450" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="550" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-5b013417dff3db79bf706e58fac23f62_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='550'%20height='450'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="550" data-rawheight="450" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="550" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-5b013417dff3db79bf706e58fac23f62_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-5b013417dff3db79bf706e58fac23f62_b.jpg"></figure><p><br></p><p>2. 翩翩起舞：Bounden（适合10分钟以上游戏时间）</p><p>这是一款被单身狗厌恶的游戏，同时又是一款撩妹神器。两名玩家需要各自握住手机的一端，并翩翩起舞，通过身体的移动，让屏幕上的指针击中连串的目标小球。在你完成游戏的同时，你和ta也完成了一支完整的舞蹈。</p><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-0e103c091a9cbb83a1a41cd3a5ea6349_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="512" data-rawheight="288" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="512" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-0e103c091a9cbb83a1a41cd3a5ea6349_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='512'%20height='288'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="512" data-rawheight="288" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="512" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-0e103c091a9cbb83a1a41cd3a5ea6349_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-0e103c091a9cbb83a1a41cd3a5ea6349_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-793c85e373683284d8d40fa0857cd7dd_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="508" data-rawheight="438" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="508" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-793c85e373683284d8d40fa0857cd7dd_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='508'%20height='438'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="508" data-rawheight="438" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="508" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-793c85e373683284d8d40fa0857cd7dd_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-793c85e373683284d8d40fa0857cd7dd_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-5f399746798fccd3dc81158f3a52436c_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="480" data-rawheight="319" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="480" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-5f399746798fccd3dc81158f3a52436c_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='480'%20height='319'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="480" data-rawheight="319" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="480" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-5f399746798fccd3dc81158f3a52436c_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-5f399746798fccd3dc81158f3a52436c_b.jpg"></figure><p><br></p><p>3. 信任的进化（适合20分钟以上游戏时间）</p><p>这是一个以经济学博弈论为理论基础制作的一款小游戏，讲述了人类之间的不信任为什么传播的越来越广。不具有什么游戏性，却是一个发人深省的好游戏。你会觉得花时间去玩这款游戏非常的值。</p><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-741da3d573860885d5d0ebdc6c018a40_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="1361" data-rawheight="553" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1361" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-741da3d573860885d5d0ebdc6c018a40_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1361'%20height='553'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="1361" data-rawheight="553" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="1361" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-741da3d573860885d5d0ebdc6c018a40_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-741da3d573860885d5d0ebdc6c018a40_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-9e211223216803e25592a517cccdf579_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="1364" data-rawheight="547" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1364" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-9e211223216803e25592a517cccdf579_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1364'%20height='547'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="1364" data-rawheight="547" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="1364" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-9e211223216803e25592a517cccdf579_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-9e211223216803e25592a517cccdf579_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-d35cfa8a0aa571df5f97c82a0b215ec7_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="1357" data-rawheight="546" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1357" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-d35cfa8a0aa571df5f97c82a0b215ec7_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1357'%20height='546'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="1357" data-rawheight="546" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="1357" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-d35cfa8a0aa571df5f97c82a0b215ec7_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-d35cfa8a0aa571df5f97c82a0b215ec7_b.jpg"></figure><p><br></p><p>4.投影寻真：shadowmatic（有5分钟就能玩）</p><p>荣获Apple设计大奖，游戏中玩家需要操纵和移动一些悬浮在空中较为抽象的、看不出本体的物品，通过灯光投影的方式在墙上投射出一个它们组合而成的真面目。游戏画面精美，设计精巧，能够完全激发你的想象力，给你带来无限惊喜。</p><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-48c4867c6b2e2ef5462c906e35865f50_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="600" data-rawheight="337" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="600" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-48c4867c6b2e2ef5462c906e35865f50_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='600'%20height='337'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="600" data-rawheight="337" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="600" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-48c4867c6b2e2ef5462c906e35865f50_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-48c4867c6b2e2ef5462c906e35865f50_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-6009a2cc0fbefa1b33eb01e26e1822fe_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="480" data-rawheight="270" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="480" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-6009a2cc0fbefa1b33eb01e26e1822fe_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='480'%20height='270'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="480" data-rawheight="270" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="480" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-6009a2cc0fbefa1b33eb01e26e1822fe_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-6009a2cc0fbefa1b33eb01e26e1822fe_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-7791f3e69831c3f767ad62c7015cc45e_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="500" data-rawheight="375" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="500" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-7791f3e69831c3f767ad62c7015cc45e_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='500'%20height='375'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="500" data-rawheight="375" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="500" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-7791f3e69831c3f767ad62c7015cc45e_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-7791f3e69831c3f767ad62c7015cc45e_b.jpg"></figure><p><br></p><p>5. 妈妈把我的游戏藏起来了系列（有5分钟就能玩）</p><p>这是一个需要和妈妈斗智斗勇的游戏，玩家需要在房间中想尽办法找到妈妈藏起来的游戏机。超级无厘头，但又让人感觉很轻松，脑洞大开的游戏。</p><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-e3fc9703e97090edacb4ef94d2e86330_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="1472" data-rawheight="828" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1472" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-e3fc9703e97090edacb4ef94d2e86330_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1472'%20height='828'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="1472" data-rawheight="828" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="1472" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-e3fc9703e97090edacb4ef94d2e86330_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-e3fc9703e97090edacb4ef94d2e86330_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-8f3034c553d5f70ca019b5ba9e48a9c2_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="1468" data-rawheight="1300" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1468" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-8f3034c553d5f70ca019b5ba9e48a9c2_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1468'%20height='1300'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="1468" data-rawheight="1300" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="1468" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-8f3034c553d5f70ca019b5ba9e48a9c2_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-8f3034c553d5f70ca019b5ba9e48a9c2_b.jpg"></figure><p><br></p><p>6.彩墨弹球：INKS.（适合10分钟以上游戏时间）</p><p>游戏结合了探求游戏的乐趣和一系列的策略挑战，随着弹球在画布上横冲直撞，玩家就能创作出独一无二的艺术品。画面绚丽多彩，给玩家带来了美妙的视觉冲击。</p><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-8afc386b568ebaeef699949903a551f8_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="500" data-rawheight="333" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="500" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-8afc386b568ebaeef699949903a551f8_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='500'%20height='333'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="500" data-rawheight="333" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="500" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-8afc386b568ebaeef699949903a551f8_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-8afc386b568ebaeef699949903a551f8_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-c71d8e9cbb745e4228504403e2fc3862_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="500" data-rawheight="428" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="500" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-c71d8e9cbb745e4228504403e2fc3862_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='500'%20height='428'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="500" data-rawheight="428" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="500" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-c71d8e9cbb745e4228504403e2fc3862_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-c71d8e9cbb745e4228504403e2fc3862_b.jpg"></figure><p>7. 狂动物园（有5分钟就能玩）</p><p>将跑酷与收集，经营结合在一起，玩家需要在跑酷的过程中抓捕动作，并扩张自己的动物园，值得一提的是，游戏一直保持着更新，让玩家不断地保持着对游戏的新鲜感。</p><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-1700a2afbf5de1ce81bba7d04cb0094d_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="500" data-rawheight="336" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="500" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-1700a2afbf5de1ce81bba7d04cb0094d_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='500'%20height='336'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="500" data-rawheight="336" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="500" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-1700a2afbf5de1ce81bba7d04cb0094d_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-1700a2afbf5de1ce81bba7d04cb0094d_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-b592eb2d647d80ac0ff259d8138a9d9f_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="500" data-rawheight="333" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="500" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-b592eb2d647d80ac0ff259d8138a9d9f_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='500'%20height='333'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="500" data-rawheight="333" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="500" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-b592eb2d647d80ac0ff259d8138a9d9f_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-b592eb2d647d80ac0ff259d8138a9d9f_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-caefb73845bba304529d1ca4ada38d94_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="498" data-rawheight="331" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="498" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-caefb73845bba304529d1ca4ada38d94_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='498'%20height='331'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="498" data-rawheight="331" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="498" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-caefb73845bba304529d1ca4ada38d94_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-caefb73845bba304529d1ca4ada38d94_b.jpg"></figure><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><b>【解谜类游戏】</b></p><p>1. 爷爷的城市：Lumino City（适合30分钟以上的游戏时间）</p><p>荣获多项游戏视觉奖项，游戏场景全部由工作室手工搭建，游戏美如画，每一帧都是壁纸，一眼就让你爱上这款游戏。故事主线温馨有爱，拥有初中游戏画面的同时不忘解谜游戏的核心，谜题设计也十分用心，让你游戏在爷爷的城市中无法自拔。</p><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-ff941b9fac7de7c0678f55105f6703f2_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="900" data-rawheight="500" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="900" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-ff941b9fac7de7c0678f55105f6703f2_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='900'%20height='500'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="900" data-rawheight="500" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="900" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-ff941b9fac7de7c0678f55105f6703f2_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-ff941b9fac7de7c0678f55105f6703f2_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-38dbdfaf4e6543f6ceb678de4acfbaea_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="633" data-rawheight="352" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="633" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-38dbdfaf4e6543f6ceb678de4acfbaea_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='633'%20height='352'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="633" data-rawheight="352" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="633" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-38dbdfaf4e6543f6ceb678de4acfbaea_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-38dbdfaf4e6543f6ceb678de4acfbaea_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-f12730e54f398025641e2e5a2abee2e9_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="550" data-rawheight="285" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="550" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-f12730e54f398025641e2e5a2abee2e9_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='550'%20height='285'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="550" data-rawheight="285" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="550" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-f12730e54f398025641e2e5a2abee2e9_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-f12730e54f398025641e2e5a2abee2e9_b.jpg"></figure><p><br></p><p>2. 回声探路：Dark Echo（适合10分钟以上游戏时间）</p><p>解谜界的一股清流，放弃了对游戏画面的追求，转而追求对听觉的刺激。身处迷宫却看不到迷宫，让玩家在未知中通过声波的反射探索迷宫的出路。非常富有创新的一款游戏，建议带上耳机，会有身临其境的感觉。</p><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-aca643f3d84044eca936cc0dc1e5b47d_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="900" data-rawheight="500" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="900" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-aca643f3d84044eca936cc0dc1e5b47d_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='900'%20height='500'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="900" data-rawheight="500" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="900" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-aca643f3d84044eca936cc0dc1e5b47d_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-aca643f3d84044eca936cc0dc1e5b47d_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-26939e56ab21a232b53b2e7acfe1c191_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="900" data-rawheight="506" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="900" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-26939e56ab21a232b53b2e7acfe1c191_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='900'%20height='506'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="900" data-rawheight="506" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="900" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-26939e56ab21a232b53b2e7acfe1c191_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-26939e56ab21a232b53b2e7acfe1c191_b.jpg"></figure><p><br></p><p>3. 全心爱你：love you to bits（适合15分钟以上游戏时间）</p><p>解谜游戏《小小盗贼》的精神续作，主角为了机器女友探寻宇宙各个角落，演绎永恒的爱情。游戏画面呈现卡通风格，十分清新可爱，每个星球的场景各不相同，设计用心。游戏中富有许多彩蛋，令人爱不释手的好游戏。</p><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-8b08b99ed67bd3e46d9352da81bccec2_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="900" data-rawheight="582" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="900" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-8b08b99ed67bd3e46d9352da81bccec2_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='900'%20height='582'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="900" data-rawheight="582" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="900" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-8b08b99ed67bd3e46d9352da81bccec2_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-8b08b99ed67bd3e46d9352da81bccec2_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-90fea1208b756637e9624906afb5829c_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="900" data-rawheight="584" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="900" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-90fea1208b756637e9624906afb5829c_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='900'%20height='584'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="900" data-rawheight="584" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="900" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-90fea1208b756637e9624906afb5829c_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-90fea1208b756637e9624906afb5829c_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-066ceee44c91475cc0491b9f5ae10d83_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="900" data-rawheight="506" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="900" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-066ceee44c91475cc0491b9f5ae10d83_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='900'%20height='506'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="900" data-rawheight="506" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="900" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-066ceee44c91475cc0491b9f5ae10d83_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-066ceee44c91475cc0491b9f5ae10d83_b.jpg"></figure><p><br></p><p>4. 纪念碑谷1、2（适合15分钟以上游戏时间）</p><p>自从这款游戏诞生，推荐解谜游戏再也绕不开它。唯美的游戏画面，利用视觉误差设计的精妙机关，富有深意的台词和剧情。给玩家带来的震撼总是无法令人忘怀，游戏过后的那份感动长存于心。</p><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-573c867bff2a3dc5330b2c12a1ee1440_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="500" data-rawheight="348" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="500" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-573c867bff2a3dc5330b2c12a1ee1440_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='500'%20height='348'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="500" data-rawheight="348" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="500" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-573c867bff2a3dc5330b2c12a1ee1440_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-573c867bff2a3dc5330b2c12a1ee1440_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-e3ff3141692b1d8b86571983b1a6b2c4_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="600" data-rawheight="380" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="600" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-e3ff3141692b1d8b86571983b1a6b2c4_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='600'%20height='380'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="600" data-rawheight="380" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="600" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-e3ff3141692b1d8b86571983b1a6b2c4_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-e3ff3141692b1d8b86571983b1a6b2c4_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-63e62aa6fb5a8c81084e16a904fd9615_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="613" data-rawheight="300" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="613" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-63e62aa6fb5a8c81084e16a904fd9615_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='613'%20height='300'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="613" data-rawheight="300" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="613" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-63e62aa6fb5a8c81084e16a904fd9615_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-63e62aa6fb5a8c81084e16a904fd9615_b.jpg"></figure><p><br></p><p>5. 致命框架1、2：FRAMED（适合15分钟以上游戏时间）</p><p>游戏的画面及背景音乐制作精良，配合上极具创意的游戏玩法，通过移动漫画分镜来演绎不同的过程和结果。在不断地推导和尝试之后，看到主角过关依旧能够惊叹于游戏设计的精妙和令人意想不到之处。</p><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-664e243420183dbb83001d214ae2890a_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="500" data-rawheight="281" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="500" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-664e243420183dbb83001d214ae2890a_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='500'%20height='281'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="500" data-rawheight="281" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="500" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-664e243420183dbb83001d214ae2890a_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-664e243420183dbb83001d214ae2890a_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-8ada983be9982ffb1f172b7238c7acf2_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="512" data-rawheight="287" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="512" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-8ada983be9982ffb1f172b7238c7acf2_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='512'%20height='287'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="512" data-rawheight="287" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="512" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-8ada983be9982ffb1f172b7238c7acf2_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-8ada983be9982ffb1f172b7238c7acf2_b.jpg"></figure><p><br></p><p>6. 未上锁的房间系列：The room（适合30分钟以上游戏时间）</p><p>第一次玩这款游戏的时候，一脸震惊。游戏需要通过解开盒子内的机关来逃出房间，但这盒子也太精美了吧，这机关设计环环相扣，也太巧妙了吧。绝对是喜欢解谜的玩家不该错过的一款游戏。</p><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-8fb6a34c018a2b34310236adbcff0bfe_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="500" data-rawheight="334" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="500" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-8fb6a34c018a2b34310236adbcff0bfe_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='500'%20height='334'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="500" data-rawheight="334" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="500" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-8fb6a34c018a2b34310236adbcff0bfe_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-8fb6a34c018a2b34310236adbcff0bfe_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-8ccc99963ce041601f757f5c1a5a570d_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="480" data-rawheight="270" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="480" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-8ccc99963ce041601f757f5c1a5a570d_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='480'%20height='270'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="480" data-rawheight="270" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="480" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-8ccc99963ce041601f757f5c1a5a570d_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-8ccc99963ce041601f757f5c1a5a570d_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-8a8a62ff24a468f07fc3e8f78f95300b_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="568" data-rawheight="320" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="568" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-8a8a62ff24a468f07fc3e8f78f95300b_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='568'%20height='320'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="568" data-rawheight="320" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="568" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-8a8a62ff24a468f07fc3e8f78f95300b_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-8a8a62ff24a468f07fc3e8f78f95300b_b.jpg"></figure><p><br></p><p>7. 迷失岛（适合30分钟以上游戏时间）</p><p>2016年ios最佳独立游戏。你被困在一座孤岛上，需要你来解开这座孤岛的秘密。游戏的谜题很棒（说实话，有点难），外星文明和地球文明的结合让这座岛充满了神秘感，让玩家迫切的想要解开岛上的谜题。温馨提示：二周目有惊喜哦。</p><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-7de2b3f4ccea1e80da3757e9c94ea11f_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="500" data-rawheight="280" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="500" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-7de2b3f4ccea1e80da3757e9c94ea11f_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='500'%20height='280'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="500" data-rawheight="280" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="500" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-7de2b3f4ccea1e80da3757e9c94ea11f_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-7de2b3f4ccea1e80da3757e9c94ea11f_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-34c5fad41e56247fe5137fabac7216d4_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="550" data-rawheight="308" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="550" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-34c5fad41e56247fe5137fabac7216d4_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='550'%20height='308'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="550" data-rawheight="308" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="550" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-34c5fad41e56247fe5137fabac7216d4_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-34c5fad41e56247fe5137fabac7216d4_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-6e481c47b79ed9c658f6b4227b9afcb5_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="550" data-rawheight="309" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="550" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-6e481c47b79ed9c658f6b4227b9afcb5_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='550'%20height='309'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="550" data-rawheight="309" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="550" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-6e481c47b79ed9c658f6b4227b9afcb5_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-6e481c47b79ed9c658f6b4227b9afcb5_b.jpg"></figure><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><b>【动作冒险】</b></p><p>1. 聚爆：implosion（适合20分钟以上游戏时间）</p><p>科幻类题材ARPG，游戏画面效果极佳，并拥有超强<a href="https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//baike.baidu.com/item/%25E6%2589%2593%25E5%2587%25BB%25E6%2584%259F" class=" wrap external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">打击感</a>。游戏富有冲击力的人物场景与超快节奏的打斗给玩家们带来血脉贲张之感。总之一个字：爽！</p><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-72673e37b941342c39e5a7c3894fa702_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="625" data-rawheight="300" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="625" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-72673e37b941342c39e5a7c3894fa702_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='625'%20height='300'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="625" data-rawheight="300" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="625" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-72673e37b941342c39e5a7c3894fa702_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-72673e37b941342c39e5a7c3894fa702_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-f00bb9b58061e3ad7ea39c53f45bb445_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="800" data-rawheight="480" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="800" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-f00bb9b58061e3ad7ea39c53f45bb445_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='800'%20height='480'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="800" data-rawheight="480" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="800" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-f00bb9b58061e3ad7ea39c53f45bb445_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-f00bb9b58061e3ad7ea39c53f45bb445_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-bc29b22fe464f93265d7cfffd5724b08_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="800" data-rawheight="480" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="800" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-bc29b22fe464f93265d7cfffd5724b08_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='800'%20height='480'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="800" data-rawheight="480" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="800" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-bc29b22fe464f93265d7cfffd5724b08_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-bc29b22fe464f93265d7cfffd5724b08_b.jpg"></figure><p><br></p><p>2. 艾希：icey（适合30分钟以上游戏时间）</p><p>在steam上被誉为国产游戏之光的《艾希》在近日登录了移动平台。流畅的打斗动作，酷炫的连招，以及游戏中的meta元素，为它赢得了广大玩家的好评。（meta，简单点说就是能让你感受到跨越次元的感觉）</p><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-bd6a6bf1b824b9fb89153a5ac3d57a3d_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="900" data-rawheight="500" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="900" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-bd6a6bf1b824b9fb89153a5ac3d57a3d_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='900'%20height='500'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="900" data-rawheight="500" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="900" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-bd6a6bf1b824b9fb89153a5ac3d57a3d_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-bd6a6bf1b824b9fb89153a5ac3d57a3d_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-56aa265cea260db0ece986da0c92207c_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="900" data-rawheight="506" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="900" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-56aa265cea260db0ece986da0c92207c_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='900'%20height='506'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="900" data-rawheight="506" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="900" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-56aa265cea260db0ece986da0c92207c_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-56aa265cea260db0ece986da0c92207c_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-c56eac7e32997129a8e9b81d089bc2f8_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="900" data-rawheight="506" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="900" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-c56eac7e32997129a8e9b81d089bc2f8_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='900'%20height='506'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="900" data-rawheight="506" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="900" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-c56eac7e32997129a8e9b81d089bc2f8_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-c56eac7e32997129a8e9b81d089bc2f8_b.jpg"></figure><p><br></p><p>3. 元气骑士（适合10分钟以上游戏时间）</p><p>超棒的动作射击游戏，十分考验玩家的走位，丰富的武器系统，不同角色的技能设定，让你百玩不腻。游戏还支持局域网内联机，安卓和ios的小伙伴也能一起打boss啦。不仅如此，游戏到目前为止还在不断地更新角色和武器哦。</p><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-df07946b994698bbed36967c70af769b_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="500" data-rawheight="275" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="500" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-df07946b994698bbed36967c70af769b_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='500'%20height='275'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="500" data-rawheight="275" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="500" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-df07946b994698bbed36967c70af769b_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-df07946b994698bbed36967c70af769b_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-449de6be94d52bebc35901367efa904f_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="1280" data-rawheight="720" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1280" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-449de6be94d52bebc35901367efa904f_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1280'%20height='720'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="1280" data-rawheight="720" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="1280" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-449de6be94d52bebc35901367efa904f_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-449de6be94d52bebc35901367efa904f_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-70bba900b44264b27a0455d81fd4d32c_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="1280" data-rawheight="720" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1280" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-70bba900b44264b27a0455d81fd4d32c_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1280'%20height='720'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="1280" data-rawheight="720" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="1280" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-70bba900b44264b27a0455d81fd4d32c_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-70bba900b44264b27a0455d81fd4d32c_b.jpg"></figure><p><br></p><p>4. 破碎大陆系列: Badland（适合10分钟以上游戏时间）</p><p>玩家需要躲避致命的元素，在手绘风格的魔幻世界中飞行并生存，体验充满想象力的陷阱、谜题和障碍带给你的乐趣， 最终飞向安全之地。游戏画面唯美，如果我没记错的话，游戏还支持同屏多人一起玩耍。</p><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-7897138364742170555588931aa683b1_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="705" data-rawheight="334" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="705" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-7897138364742170555588931aa683b1_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='705'%20height='334'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="705" data-rawheight="334" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="705" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-7897138364742170555588931aa683b1_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-7897138364742170555588931aa683b1_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-095e0d7bc5d0318b9be7fab921d0d593_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="480" data-rawheight="270" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="480" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-095e0d7bc5d0318b9be7fab921d0d593_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='480'%20height='270'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="480" data-rawheight="270" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="480" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-095e0d7bc5d0318b9be7fab921d0d593_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-095e0d7bc5d0318b9be7fab921d0d593_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-d7026bbe4e83538442298d900dc21ff2_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="480" data-rawheight="270" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="480" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-d7026bbe4e83538442298d900dc21ff2_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='480'%20height='270'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="480" data-rawheight="270" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="480" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-d7026bbe4e83538442298d900dc21ff2_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-d7026bbe4e83538442298d900dc21ff2_b.jpg"></figure><p><br></p><p>5. 龙之丘系列: dragon hills（有5分钟就能玩）</p><p>玩家需要操控一只危险的巨龙来帮助愤怒的公主完成复仇之旅。巨龙从山丘掠下,在地上与地下之间穿梭,粉碎和摧毁一切障碍，给玩家带来了破坏的快感。拥有刺激的boss战和丰富的技能升级路线，是一款不容易使玩家感到厌倦的游戏。</p><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-b5213be7ab1652b0babf459c3707154c_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="500" data-rawheight="300" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="500" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-b5213be7ab1652b0babf459c3707154c_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='500'%20height='300'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="500" data-rawheight="300" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="500" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-b5213be7ab1652b0babf459c3707154c_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-b5213be7ab1652b0babf459c3707154c_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-6d97e06451896c7b52316febace2efb3_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="430" data-rawheight="242" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="430" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-6d97e06451896c7b52316febace2efb3_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='430'%20height='242'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="430" data-rawheight="242" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="430" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-6d97e06451896c7b52316febace2efb3_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-6d97e06451896c7b52316febace2efb3_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-cfaeefbc11a394588a1086d02fa7144c_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="600" data-rawheight="311" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="600" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-cfaeefbc11a394588a1086d02fa7144c_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='600'%20height='311'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="600" data-rawheight="311" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="600" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-cfaeefbc11a394588a1086d02fa7144c_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-cfaeefbc11a394588a1086d02fa7144c_b.jpg"></figure><p><br></p><p>6. 暗影格斗（有5分钟就能玩）</p><p>纵使游戏人物没有五官，你也能够通过流畅的打斗动作甚至它的呼吸感受到游戏人物的真实，玩家需要不断去挑战更强的人物来为自己的角色解锁新的武器。游戏的武术动作真的超赞，有种看武侠片的感觉。</p><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-92be061aa011bb98f062d157c4243d76_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="500" data-rawheight="325" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="500" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-92be061aa011bb98f062d157c4243d76_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='500'%20height='325'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="500" data-rawheight="325" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="500" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-92be061aa011bb98f062d157c4243d76_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-92be061aa011bb98f062d157c4243d76_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-d1e6cdecbf2a4c7b192c27ab096ae047_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="1600" data-rawheight="900" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1600" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-d1e6cdecbf2a4c7b192c27ab096ae047_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1600'%20height='900'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="1600" data-rawheight="900" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="1600" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-d1e6cdecbf2a4c7b192c27ab096ae047_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-d1e6cdecbf2a4c7b192c27ab096ae047_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-9ed3c28d9422c53bc804956fefbd6279_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="1024" data-rawheight="577" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1024" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-9ed3c28d9422c53bc804956fefbd6279_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1024'%20height='577'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="1024" data-rawheight="577" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="1024" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-9ed3c28d9422c53bc804956fefbd6279_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-9ed3c28d9422c53bc804956fefbd6279_b.jpg"></figure><p><br></p><p><b>【生存类游戏】</b></p><p>1. 这是我的战争：this war of mine（适合30分钟以上游戏时间）</p><p>荣获超过100项游戏奖项。讲述了战争世界中的生活。玩家需要扮演战后的平民在世界中生存下来，战后世界中充斥着性格家迥异的生存者，不仅考验玩家对于生存的理解，还引发了玩家对于人性的思考---战争没有赢家。</p><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-5ff9811a58213310bd097eb4ad90da30_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="500" data-rawheight="275" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="500" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-5ff9811a58213310bd097eb4ad90da30_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='500'%20height='275'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="500" data-rawheight="275" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="500" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-5ff9811a58213310bd097eb4ad90da30_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-5ff9811a58213310bd097eb4ad90da30_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-ffc51deb45ad79e7caa9a2c4ccc404a1_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="1334" data-rawheight="750" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1334" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-ffc51deb45ad79e7caa9a2c4ccc404a1_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1334'%20height='750'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="1334" data-rawheight="750" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="1334" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-ffc51deb45ad79e7caa9a2c4ccc404a1_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-ffc51deb45ad79e7caa9a2c4ccc404a1_b.jpg"></figure><p><br></p><p>2. 饥荒：Don’t Starve（适合30分钟以上游戏时间）</p><p>想必这个游戏并不需要我过多的介绍。从pc到移动平台，游戏依然保持了精良的品质。玩家需要在这个光怪陆离的世界中利用收集到的材料生存下来，制造生活必需品，并最终找寻回家的路。游戏在移动端的操作优化还是很不错的，可以放心食用。</p><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-01d2dc7d4f97d9b9758056d1ed72f368_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="548" data-rawheight="280" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="548" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-01d2dc7d4f97d9b9758056d1ed72f368_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='548'%20height='280'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="548" data-rawheight="280" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="548" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-01d2dc7d4f97d9b9758056d1ed72f368_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-01d2dc7d4f97d9b9758056d1ed72f368_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-45e815e2a8b0e7f4221d1c66e6366a81_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="500" data-rawheight="378" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="500" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-45e815e2a8b0e7f4221d1c66e6366a81_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='500'%20height='378'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="500" data-rawheight="378" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="500" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-45e815e2a8b0e7f4221d1c66e6366a81_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-45e815e2a8b0e7f4221d1c66e6366a81_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-85d50d29136099762c94fb16314dbfea_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="640" data-rawheight="360" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="640" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-85d50d29136099762c94fb16314dbfea_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='640'%20height='360'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="640" data-rawheight="360" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="640" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-85d50d29136099762c94fb16314dbfea_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-85d50d29136099762c94fb16314dbfea_b.jpg"></figure><p><br></p><p>3. 归家异途（适合20分钟以上游戏时间）</p><p>这是一款由中国团队打造的roguelike游戏（每一次游戏的所有事物都是随机的），玩家将扮演因为战争和女儿失散的难民，一路前行，收集各类物资生存下去并对付来犯的叛军和凶猛生物，最终找到自己的失散的家人。</p><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-405e2d89128dfb21ae699a4c2d4c7c0e_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="1920" data-rawheight="1080" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1920" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-405e2d89128dfb21ae699a4c2d4c7c0e_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1920'%20height='1080'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="1920" data-rawheight="1080" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="1920" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-405e2d89128dfb21ae699a4c2d4c7c0e_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-405e2d89128dfb21ae699a4c2d4c7c0e_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-e9ba613c357a9c6608ecbdcf484b8b39_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="1280" data-rawheight="720" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1280" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-e9ba613c357a9c6608ecbdcf484b8b39_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1280'%20height='720'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="1280" data-rawheight="720" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="1280" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-e9ba613c357a9c6608ecbdcf484b8b39_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-e9ba613c357a9c6608ecbdcf484b8b39_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-ab16ee80a754607a125ecf74cf7e9762_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="1132" data-rawheight="635" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1132" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-ab16ee80a754607a125ecf74cf7e9762_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1132'%20height='635'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="1132" data-rawheight="635" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="1132" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-ab16ee80a754607a125ecf74cf7e9762_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-ab16ee80a754607a125ecf74cf7e9762_b.jpg"></figure><p><br></p><p>4. 崩溃大陆：Crashlands（适合30分钟以上游戏时间）</p><p>一款类似但不同于饥荒的游戏，玩家可以建造自己的家园，养育自己的宠物并让其跟随你战斗，游戏拥有自己的主线剧情，不会让玩家觉得漫无目的。游戏丰富的道具和制造系统让玩家即便不随着剧情走也能乐此不疲。</p><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-7cb12d3d44a9a60de12e02306b0808f9_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="1733" data-rawheight="1083" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1733" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-7cb12d3d44a9a60de12e02306b0808f9_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1733'%20height='1083'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="1733" data-rawheight="1083" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="1733" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-7cb12d3d44a9a60de12e02306b0808f9_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-7cb12d3d44a9a60de12e02306b0808f9_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-a960d5a10771ddd9af34f45a89f2959a_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="1920" data-rawheight="1080" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1920" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-a960d5a10771ddd9af34f45a89f2959a_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1920'%20height='1080'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="1920" data-rawheight="1080" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="1920" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-a960d5a10771ddd9af34f45a89f2959a_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-a960d5a10771ddd9af34f45a89f2959a_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-51c42b7df4b7e1722db11b726d760d66_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="1764" data-rawheight="992" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1764" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-51c42b7df4b7e1722db11b726d760d66_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1764'%20height='992'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="1764" data-rawheight="992" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="1764" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-51c42b7df4b7e1722db11b726d760d66_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-51c42b7df4b7e1722db11b726d760d66_b.jpg"></figure><p><br></p><p>5. 辐射岛（适合30分钟以上游戏时间）</p><p>玩家所扮演的主角身在一个空无人烟的岛屿当中，身边有各种设施却看不到任何一个活人，于是只能一边的通过岛上的可用资源生存，一边往岛的深处探索，将这个岛屿深埋于地下的秘密挖掘出来。游戏画面十分真实，自由度非常高，让玩家充满了探索的欲望。</p><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-fc30b466c3a366701b8f0bbe509b5643_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="1072" data-rawheight="669" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1072" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-fc30b466c3a366701b8f0bbe509b5643_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1072'%20height='669'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="1072" data-rawheight="669" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="1072" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-fc30b466c3a366701b8f0bbe509b5643_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-fc30b466c3a366701b8f0bbe509b5643_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-523d9964f3b7868393a994131d043ac1_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="1920" data-rawheight="1080" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1920" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-523d9964f3b7868393a994131d043ac1_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1920'%20height='1080'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="1920" data-rawheight="1080" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="1920" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-523d9964f3b7868393a994131d043ac1_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-523d9964f3b7868393a994131d043ac1_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-213ddbe9b513f5d324fb627ae301982e_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="550" data-rawheight="309" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="550" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-213ddbe9b513f5d324fb627ae301982e_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='550'%20height='309'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="550" data-rawheight="309" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="550" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-213ddbe9b513f5d324fb627ae301982e_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-213ddbe9b513f5d324fb627ae301982e_b.jpg"></figure><p><br></p><p><b>【经营策略】</b></p><p>1. 迷你地铁：Mini Metro（适合10分钟以上游戏时间）</p><p>Ios2016年度最佳游戏。玩家需要扮演城市地铁的建造者，为不断扩张的城市规划合适的地铁线路和站点，非常考验玩家的即时策略能力。游戏的画面非常简约，但是一旦上手，会深深被这个游戏所吸引。</p><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-a824736ca3420221bb65252f76a5c3d3_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="460" data-rawheight="215" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="460" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-a824736ca3420221bb65252f76a5c3d3_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='460'%20height='215'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="460" data-rawheight="215" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="460" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-a824736ca3420221bb65252f76a5c3d3_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-a824736ca3420221bb65252f76a5c3d3_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-5f35c088e559fd206364421a8229e8de_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="1000" data-rawheight="562" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1000" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-5f35c088e559fd206364421a8229e8de_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1000'%20height='562'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="1000" data-rawheight="562" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="1000" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-5f35c088e559fd206364421a8229e8de_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-5f35c088e559fd206364421a8229e8de_b.jpg"></figure><p><br></p><p>2. 瘟疫公司：Plague Inc.（适合10分钟以上游戏时间）</p><p>这次你不是拯救世界的英雄，而是毁灭世界的大反派。你需要制造全世界最厉害的瘟疫病毒，与科学家斗智斗勇，让瘟疫攻占整个地球，摧毁全人类。游戏很容易上手，也很容易上瘾。</p><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-ecb932fff45b5d816cc59c4070201408_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="520" data-rawheight="293" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="520" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-ecb932fff45b5d816cc59c4070201408_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='520'%20height='293'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="520" data-rawheight="293" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="520" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-ecb932fff45b5d816cc59c4070201408_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-ecb932fff45b5d816cc59c4070201408_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-49ccc21f5968cc98ca048104cd33476c_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="520" data-rawheight="293" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="520" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-49ccc21f5968cc98ca048104cd33476c_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='520'%20height='293'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="520" data-rawheight="293" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="520" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-49ccc21f5968cc98ca048104cd33476c_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-49ccc21f5968cc98ca048104cd33476c_b.jpg"></figure><p><br></p><p>3. 王国保卫战系列：Kindom Rush（适合10分钟以上游戏时间）</p><p>我心目中最棒的塔防游戏，没有之一。玩家需要通过在地图上建造炮塔或类似建筑物，来阻止游戏中敌人进攻，除了炮塔，玩家还拥有自己的英雄，他们拥有不同技能，敌军的种类也多种多样，玩家需要有效的方法去应对属性各不相同的敌人，可玩性非常的高。</p><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-911c88e286ad4828b244f9a3272dd917_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="1920" data-rawheight="1080" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1920" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-911c88e286ad4828b244f9a3272dd917_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1920'%20height='1080'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="1920" data-rawheight="1080" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="1920" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-911c88e286ad4828b244f9a3272dd917_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-911c88e286ad4828b244f9a3272dd917_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-f188241ac81d487702caf9d5e90ceb58_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="480" data-rawheight="320" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="480" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-f188241ac81d487702caf9d5e90ceb58_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='480'%20height='320'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="480" data-rawheight="320" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="480" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-f188241ac81d487702caf9d5e90ceb58_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-f188241ac81d487702caf9d5e90ceb58_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-150de3f9242b0fd79beb52ff716aecc4_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="1800" data-rawheight="1080" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1800" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-150de3f9242b0fd79beb52ff716aecc4_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1800'%20height='1080'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="1800" data-rawheight="1080" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="1800" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-150de3f9242b0fd79beb52ff716aecc4_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-150de3f9242b0fd79beb52ff716aecc4_b.jpg"></figure><p><br></p><p>4. 辐射 避难所（适合20分钟以上游戏时间）</p><p>玩家需要管理并扩张一个存在于地下的高科技避难所。你需要让避难所中的居民开心的存活下来，让他们去建造，去地面探索，去繁衍他们的下一代。除此之外玩家还需要抵御外来生物的入侵，应对突如其来的意外灾害。</p><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-1ff08857024579876422ed76a28ad6f2_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="1920" data-rawheight="820" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1920" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-1ff08857024579876422ed76a28ad6f2_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1920'%20height='820'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="1920" data-rawheight="820" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="1920" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-1ff08857024579876422ed76a28ad6f2_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-1ff08857024579876422ed76a28ad6f2_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-e21a4f4ad8ae8140c28879486db5e670_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="1267" data-rawheight="713" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1267" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-e21a4f4ad8ae8140c28879486db5e670_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1267'%20height='713'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="1267" data-rawheight="713" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="1267" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-e21a4f4ad8ae8140c28879486db5e670_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-e21a4f4ad8ae8140c28879486db5e670_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-f1855cbd79e5b36190146076b4309190_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="600" data-rawheight="338" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="600" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-f1855cbd79e5b36190146076b4309190_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='600'%20height='338'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="600" data-rawheight="338" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="600" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-f1855cbd79e5b36190146076b4309190_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-f1855cbd79e5b36190146076b4309190_b.jpg"></figure><p><br></p><p>5. 开罗游戏系列（适合10分钟以上游戏时间）</p><p>开罗出品，必属精品。开罗游戏系列拥有着体积小，像素画风却十分注重细节，游戏性很高的特点。受到几乎所有广大模拟经营类玩家的喜爱。代表作有游戏发展国，<a href="https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//baike.baidu.com/item/%25E6%259A%2596%25E6%259A%2596%25E6%25B8%25A9%25E6%25B3%2589%25E4%25B9%25A1" class=" wrap external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">暖暖温泉乡</a>，百货商店开店日记等等。</p><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-4cce0ec3a6bf5e0eb82cb1438ec0edde_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="400" data-rawheight="257" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="content_image" width="400"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='400'%20height='257'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="400" data-rawheight="257" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="content_image lazy" width="400" data-actualsrc="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-4cce0ec3a6bf5e0eb82cb1438ec0edde_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-d72a0a3c120b29268ed7a9b0e3727dff_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="480" data-rawheight="288" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="480" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-d72a0a3c120b29268ed7a9b0e3727dff_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='480'%20height='288'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="480" data-rawheight="288" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="480" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-d72a0a3c120b29268ed7a9b0e3727dff_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-d72a0a3c120b29268ed7a9b0e3727dff_b.jpg"></figure><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><b>【音乐节奏类游戏】</b></p><p>1. 古树旋律：Deemo（适合10分钟以上游戏时间）</p><p>这是一款注重剧情故事叙述的音乐类游戏，游戏将采用以钢琴旋律为主的音乐类型，为你带来一场震撼的视听盛宴。游戏的操作采用简单的触屏控制，易于上手，你要看准时机打击落下的音符。好好体验它，你会为这款游戏而感动的。</p><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-8fcc9b29d101f5387686a42670cd9063_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="480" data-rawheight="270" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="480" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-8fcc9b29d101f5387686a42670cd9063_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='480'%20height='270'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="480" data-rawheight="270" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="480" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-8fcc9b29d101f5387686a42670cd9063_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-8fcc9b29d101f5387686a42670cd9063_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-fb9221203cfa71fc694e779e744f7b70_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="2208" data-rawheight="1242" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="2208" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-fb9221203cfa71fc694e779e744f7b70_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='2208'%20height='1242'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="2208" data-rawheight="1242" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="2208" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-fb9221203cfa71fc694e779e744f7b70_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-fb9221203cfa71fc694e779e744f7b70_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-4f7f0f88f500553db4d1cdd558cf0a38_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="800" data-rawheight="480" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="800" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-4f7f0f88f500553db4d1cdd558cf0a38_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='800'%20height='480'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="800" data-rawheight="480" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="800" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-4f7f0f88f500553db4d1cdd558cf0a38_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-4f7f0f88f500553db4d1cdd558cf0a38_b.jpg"></figure><p><br></p><p>2. 音乐世界：Cytus（适合10分钟以上游戏时间）</p><p>与《古树旋律》师出同门，操作上略有不同。同为音乐游戏中的佼佼者，如果你喜欢其中一款，你就应该去试试另一款。</p><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-43501cd1d0ac11c8c9c144bbd9430fd4_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="1200" data-rawheight="676" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1200" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-43501cd1d0ac11c8c9c144bbd9430fd4_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1200'%20height='676'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="1200" data-rawheight="676" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="1200" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-43501cd1d0ac11c8c9c144bbd9430fd4_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-43501cd1d0ac11c8c9c144bbd9430fd4_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-be8732e07e023088d1d70ad2a8ffb077_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="511" data-rawheight="245" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="511" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-be8732e07e023088d1d70ad2a8ffb077_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='511'%20height='245'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="511" data-rawheight="245" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="511" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-be8732e07e023088d1d70ad2a8ffb077_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-be8732e07e023088d1d70ad2a8ffb077_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-8826da00ac1c4f892364a1988257a971_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="1280" data-rawheight="720" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1280" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-8826da00ac1c4f892364a1988257a971_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1280'%20height='720'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="1280" data-rawheight="720" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="1280" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-8826da00ac1c4f892364a1988257a971_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-8826da00ac1c4f892364a1988257a971_b.jpg"></figure><p><br></p><p>3. 永不言弃系列（有5分钟就能玩）</p><p>有点虐心的音乐类游戏。玩家需要根据音乐节奏来帮助游戏中的小墨点越过不同的关卡，在掌握节奏感的同时还十分考验玩家的手速，是十分具有挑战性的游戏。</p><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-3f224f694f792411c578514dfc830ac8_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="600" data-rawheight="360" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="600" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-3f224f694f792411c578514dfc830ac8_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='600'%20height='360'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="600" data-rawheight="360" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="600" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-3f224f694f792411c578514dfc830ac8_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-3f224f694f792411c578514dfc830ac8_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-dd22d5522332ed9812ddc025b2bb6e3d_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="533" data-rawheight="300" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="533" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-dd22d5522332ed9812ddc025b2bb6e3d_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='533'%20height='300'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="533" data-rawheight="300" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="533" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-dd22d5522332ed9812ddc025b2bb6e3d_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-dd22d5522332ed9812ddc025b2bb6e3d_b.jpg"></figure><p><br></p><p>4.脸部跳舞机： FaceDance Challenge（有5分钟就能玩）</p><p>这是一款不能当着别人的面玩的游戏，至于为什么，看截图就知道了。屏幕上会根据音乐不断掉落不同的表情，玩家需要在摄像头前做出相应的表情来获得足够高的分数。如果你不在乎你的形象，那么尽管在旁人面前打开这款游戏。</p><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-3018d4f1badaa24495e6c0d22a5081fb_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="360" data-rawheight="220" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="content_image" width="360"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='360'%20height='220'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="360" data-rawheight="220" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="content_image lazy" width="360" data-actualsrc="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-3018d4f1badaa24495e6c0d22a5081fb_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-8ac3a8f530d179eb4146d73ef83ad030_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="393" data-rawheight="293" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="content_image" width="393"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='393'%20height='293'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="393" data-rawheight="293" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="content_image lazy" width="393" data-actualsrc="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-8ac3a8f530d179eb4146d73ef83ad030_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-d124b78fe767f09ec7aa13a06ea6ace6_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="479" data-rawheight="425" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="479" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-d124b78fe767f09ec7aa13a06ea6ace6_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='479'%20height='425'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="479" data-rawheight="425" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="479" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-d124b78fe767f09ec7aa13a06ea6ace6_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-d124b78fe767f09ec7aa13a06ea6ace6_b.jpg"></figure><p>（部分图片来自百度，侵删）</p><p><br></p><p><b>最后，码字不易，希望各位点个赞犒劳一下。</b></p><p><br></p><p><b>欢迎各位关注我的公众号“手游匣”（公众号ID：youxihenhaowan）</b></p><p><br></p><p><b>不忘初心，专注单机手游评测推荐，你喜欢的样子我都有</b></p><p><br></p><p>---------------------------------------2017.11.16更新--------------------------------------------</p><p>1.回忆之旅：Old Man's Journey（适合30分钟以上游戏时间）</p><p>冒险解谜类游戏。从唯美清新的画风中就能感受到这款游戏的优秀，玩家需要通过拖动改变地形，并点击目标地点来帮助一位老爷爷去踏上他曾经去过的地方，重拾年轻时的美好回忆。谜题难度不高，很适合一个人静静的去感受这款游戏的内涵。</p><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-994000b17f84abb3041d6c2e93f90acb_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="500" data-rawheight="375" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="500" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-994000b17f84abb3041d6c2e93f90acb_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='500'%20height='375'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="500" data-rawheight="375" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="500" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-994000b17f84abb3041d6c2e93f90acb_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-994000b17f84abb3041d6c2e93f90acb_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-1c29bc1f8b89ae686c5d9d59c74bf2dc_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="1078" data-rawheight="605" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1078" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-1c29bc1f8b89ae686c5d9d59c74bf2dc_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1078'%20height='605'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="1078" data-rawheight="605" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="1078" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-1c29bc1f8b89ae686c5d9d59c74bf2dc_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-1c29bc1f8b89ae686c5d9d59c74bf2dc_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-edbb288c5d5c1edd0d41fe7136cf0eec_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="1216" data-rawheight="688" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1216" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-edbb288c5d5c1edd0d41fe7136cf0eec_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1216'%20height='688'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="1216" data-rawheight="688" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="1216" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-edbb288c5d5c1edd0d41fe7136cf0eec_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-edbb288c5d5c1edd0d41fe7136cf0eec_b.jpg"></figure><p><br></p><p>2.沉默年代：The Silent Age（适合30分钟以上游戏时间）</p><p>冒险解谜类游戏。讲述的是游戏主角穿越回70年代肩负起了拯救人类的重任。游戏画面朴素。但它依然是一款很棒的解谜游戏，作为游戏核心的谜题相当有趣，喜欢解谜的玩家不要错过了哦。</p><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-942423ac78147943784c77b927f487f5_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="512" data-rawheight="294" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="512" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-942423ac78147943784c77b927f487f5_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='512'%20height='294'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="512" data-rawheight="294" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="512" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-942423ac78147943784c77b927f487f5_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-942423ac78147943784c77b927f487f5_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-aafd8c95fe2364292960da1640fde0f3_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="480" data-rawheight="269" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="480" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-aafd8c95fe2364292960da1640fde0f3_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='480'%20height='269'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="480" data-rawheight="269" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="480" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-aafd8c95fe2364292960da1640fde0f3_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-aafd8c95fe2364292960da1640fde0f3_b.jpg"></figure><p>3.逃离方块系列：Cube Escape（适合15分钟以上游戏时间）</p><p>解谜类游戏。这款游戏比较类似是密室逃脱游戏吧，游戏不大，画面也比较一般，可是谜题设置很棒啊，而且目前出了12部，连在一起讲述了一个故事啊，很酷啊。（按剧情顺序是这样的:1.轮回的房间2.四季3.锈色湖畔4.阿尔勒5.哈维的盒子6.23号案件7.风车8.锈色旅馆9.生日10.剧院11.锈湖根源12.洞穴）</p><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-e59b77ed06996f2c3e48d449eed1108a_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="520" data-rawheight="293" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="520" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-e59b77ed06996f2c3e48d449eed1108a_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='520'%20height='293'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="520" data-rawheight="293" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="520" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-e59b77ed06996f2c3e48d449eed1108a_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-e59b77ed06996f2c3e48d449eed1108a_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-eb94d6bf06583cf8e00c10347ea1c03f_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="550" data-rawheight="308" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="550" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-eb94d6bf06583cf8e00c10347ea1c03f_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='550'%20height='308'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="550" data-rawheight="308" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="550" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-eb94d6bf06583cf8e00c10347ea1c03f_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-eb94d6bf06583cf8e00c10347ea1c03f_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-3ef0b1ad21c12c4ac02dc74781eca55b_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="800" data-rawheight="457" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="800" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-3ef0b1ad21c12c4ac02dc74781eca55b_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='800'%20height='457'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="800" data-rawheight="457" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="800" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-3ef0b1ad21c12c4ac02dc74781eca55b_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-3ef0b1ad21c12c4ac02dc74781eca55b_b.jpg"></figure><p><br></p><p>4.伪装游戏：Agent A（适合30分钟以上游戏时间）</p><p>解谜类游戏。玩家扮演的是一位特工，需要和一位间谍斗智斗勇并抓住她。游戏采用了第一人称视角，并在各个场景中配有过场动画，使得游戏很有代入感。游戏画面也十分精致，唯一的遗憾是剧情还未完结，不过游戏还在更新，最新的章节也即将放出。</p><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-9d7b83f2987715c81e9bd30251100b79_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="950" data-rawheight="713" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="950" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-9d7b83f2987715c81e9bd30251100b79_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='950'%20height='713'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="950" data-rawheight="713" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="950" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-9d7b83f2987715c81e9bd30251100b79_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-9d7b83f2987715c81e9bd30251100b79_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-707034b2b13048669ab8d7eb967669bb_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="750" data-rawheight="563" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="750" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-707034b2b13048669ab8d7eb967669bb_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='750'%20height='563'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="750" data-rawheight="563" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="750" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-707034b2b13048669ab8d7eb967669bb_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-707034b2b13048669ab8d7eb967669bb_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-f90c34bb37c5a717b1ce5ea5ea283dc1_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="600" data-rawheight="450" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="600" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-f90c34bb37c5a717b1ce5ea5ea283dc1_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='600'%20height='450'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="600" data-rawheight="450" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="600" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-f90c34bb37c5a717b1ce5ea5ea283dc1_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-f90c34bb37c5a717b1ce5ea5ea283dc1_b.jpg"></figure><p><br></p><p>5.王权：Reigns（适合10分钟以上游戏时间）</p><p>文字策略游戏。非常有趣的策略游戏，作为一位君王，你只需要单手滑动表示yes or no便可决定国家大事的走向，是不是有一种一统天下的感觉呢。不过如果决策失误的话，你的王位可是会被推翻的。</p><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-c63f74ad139586164f72832b9ee555b7_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="600" data-rawheight="533" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="600" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-c63f74ad139586164f72832b9ee555b7_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='600'%20height='533'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="600" data-rawheight="533" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="600" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-c63f74ad139586164f72832b9ee555b7_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-c63f74ad139586164f72832b9ee555b7_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-71a6e241e7301cb25111ce9e139a70a5_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="1000" data-rawheight="881" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1000" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-71a6e241e7301cb25111ce9e139a70a5_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1000'%20height='881'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="1000" data-rawheight="881" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="1000" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-71a6e241e7301cb25111ce9e139a70a5_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-71a6e241e7301cb25111ce9e139a70a5_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-c129f559634adce611dae2dc8dd33aad_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="550" data-rawheight="412" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="550" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-c129f559634adce611dae2dc8dd33aad_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='550'%20height='412'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="550" data-rawheight="412" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="550" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-c129f559634adce611dae2dc8dd33aad_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-c129f559634adce611dae2dc8dd33aad_b.jpg"></figure><p><br></p><p>6.王国：新大陆：Kingdom:New Lands（适合20分钟以上游戏时间）</p><p>策略经营。Steam广受好评的一款独立游戏，移植到移动平台之后表现依然出色。从一位穷困潦倒的国王，一步步变得富有，建立起强大的王国，成功抵御外敌的入侵。能够给玩家带来的满满的成就感。</p><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-934ac61f2efb9a7650902273d175d0a2_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="900" data-rawheight="500" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="900" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-934ac61f2efb9a7650902273d175d0a2_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='900'%20height='500'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="900" data-rawheight="500" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="900" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-934ac61f2efb9a7650902273d175d0a2_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-934ac61f2efb9a7650902273d175d0a2_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-769706af2a2e1a485ee83d96ad671d50_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="1334" data-rawheight="750" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1334" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-769706af2a2e1a485ee83d96ad671d50_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1334'%20height='750'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="1334" data-rawheight="750" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="1334" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-769706af2a2e1a485ee83d96ad671d50_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-769706af2a2e1a485ee83d96ad671d50_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-3cc1f8a09611930c94a81c0b897004d8_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="900" data-rawheight="500" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="900" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-3cc1f8a09611930c94a81c0b897004d8_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='900'%20height='500'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="900" data-rawheight="500" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="900" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-3cc1f8a09611930c94a81c0b897004d8_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-3cc1f8a09611930c94a81c0b897004d8_b.jpg"></figure><p>7.极速变色龙：Chameleon Run（适合5分钟以上游戏时间）</p><p>跑酷类游戏。游戏画面实属跑酷类游戏中的上乘之作。特殊的变色设定也给玩家带来了一定的新鲜感。关卡的设定还是有一定难度的，对自己的手速和反应有信心的玩家，是时候来挑战一下这款游戏了。</p><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-649129a1f9078bad968c5ea09476361c_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="1600" data-rawheight="900" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1600" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-649129a1f9078bad968c5ea09476361c_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1600'%20height='900'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="1600" data-rawheight="900" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="1600" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-649129a1f9078bad968c5ea09476361c_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-649129a1f9078bad968c5ea09476361c_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-25c4ffd52c22917a27a175b700053a45_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="500" data-rawheight="300" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="500" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-25c4ffd52c22917a27a175b700053a45_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='500'%20height='300'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="500" data-rawheight="300" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="500" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-25c4ffd52c22917a27a175b700053a45_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-25c4ffd52c22917a27a175b700053a45_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-13ac815ca754d680458a1f16c22e5f92_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="534" data-rawheight="300" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="534" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-13ac815ca754d680458a1f16c22e5f92_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='534'%20height='300'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="534" data-rawheight="300" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="534" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-13ac815ca754d680458a1f16c22e5f92_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-13ac815ca754d680458a1f16c22e5f92_b.jpg"></figure><p><br></p><p>8.蠢蠢的死法系列：Dumb Ways to Die（适合5分钟以上游戏时间）</p><p>算是休闲类游戏吧。游戏中融合了多款小游戏，并随着游戏的推进增加难度。游戏画面清新可爱，人物角色蠢萌蠢萌的，游戏中各种奇奇怪怪的作死方法也让玩家觉得十分有趣。是一款随时随地都适合来一发的游戏。</p><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-3f6b02e82a641f66d20f8446814847d8_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="1280" data-rawheight="720" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1280" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-3f6b02e82a641f66d20f8446814847d8_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1280'%20height='720'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="1280" data-rawheight="720" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="1280" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-3f6b02e82a641f66d20f8446814847d8_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-3f6b02e82a641f66d20f8446814847d8_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-0884cbb14580e60f5bf1213e889f3e19_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="900" data-rawheight="500" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="900" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-0884cbb14580e60f5bf1213e889f3e19_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='900'%20height='500'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="900" data-rawheight="500" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="900" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-0884cbb14580e60f5bf1213e889f3e19_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-0884cbb14580e60f5bf1213e889f3e19_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-a68cc7f0b0f7923c2a2ed2a175d0f26a_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="900" data-rawheight="506" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="900" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-a68cc7f0b0f7923c2a2ed2a175d0f26a_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='900'%20height='506'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="900" data-rawheight="506" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="900" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-a68cc7f0b0f7923c2a2ed2a175d0f26a_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-a68cc7f0b0f7923c2a2ed2a175d0f26a_b.jpg"></figure><p><br></p><p>9.模拟山羊：Goat Simulator（适合5分钟以上游戏时间）</p><p>动作冒险。玩家将化身一只山羊，在游戏中肆意的破坏。很鬼畜也很有趣的游戏。第一次觉得漫无目的的破坏也是一种乐趣啊。可以作为一款解压游戏来玩，非常适合需要在游戏中释放压力的玩家。</p><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-8a7705f54d69716ec22a6b4a0a9b609f_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="520" data-rawheight="293" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="520" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-8a7705f54d69716ec22a6b4a0a9b609f_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='520'%20height='293'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="520" data-rawheight="293" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="520" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-8a7705f54d69716ec22a6b4a0a9b609f_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-8a7705f54d69716ec22a6b4a0a9b609f_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-d2da125d53ba0e5d0bd94a65ce45ba8f_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="520" data-rawheight="293" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="520" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-d2da125d53ba0e5d0bd94a65ce45ba8f_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='520'%20height='293'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="520" data-rawheight="293" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="520" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-d2da125d53ba0e5d0bd94a65ce45ba8f_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-d2da125d53ba0e5d0bd94a65ce45ba8f_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-fd3c96d4419f43dd514904167a180d3f_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="520" data-rawheight="293" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="520" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-fd3c96d4419f43dd514904167a180d3f_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='520'%20height='293'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="520" data-rawheight="293" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="520" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-fd3c96d4419f43dd514904167a180d3f_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-fd3c96d4419f43dd514904167a180d3f_b.jpg"></figure><p><br></p><p>10.去月球：To the moon（适合30分钟以上游戏时间）</p><p>角色扮演类游戏。一款剧情向的游戏，有轻度的冒险和解谜元素。像素风格的画面，感人的bgm，结合感人至深的剧情，像是在看一部震撼人心的电影，给玩家带来无限的感动。Ios限时六折，有兴趣的玩家可以入手了。</p><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-04f95debf88dd5ce06773117f5f699df_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="1040" data-rawheight="414" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1040" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-04f95debf88dd5ce06773117f5f699df_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1040'%20height='414'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="1040" data-rawheight="414" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="1040" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-04f95debf88dd5ce06773117f5f699df_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-04f95debf88dd5ce06773117f5f699df_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-6cd72df416d4bf44769d3445eb854662_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="520" data-rawheight="293" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="520" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-6cd72df416d4bf44769d3445eb854662_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='520'%20height='293'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="520" data-rawheight="293" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="520" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-6cd72df416d4bf44769d3445eb854662_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-6cd72df416d4bf44769d3445eb854662_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-00e7a6a3071191c25d71dc2701b89f53_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="520" data-rawheight="293" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="520" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-00e7a6a3071191c25d71dc2701b89f53_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='520'%20height='293'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="520" data-rawheight="293" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="520" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-00e7a6a3071191c25d71dc2701b89f53_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-00e7a6a3071191c25d71dc2701b89f53_b.jpg"></figure><p><br></p><p>11.永不孤单：Never Alone（适合30分钟以上游戏时间）</p><p>冒险解谜游戏。在游戏中玩家将操作一位因纽特女孩和一只白狐，拯救被困在暴风雪中的部落。游戏画面精美生动，游戏中的解谜环节也给玩家带来了不少惊喜。是一款整体素质十分出色的游戏。</p><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-aa1478e3bb2abddb9ac6b62cc3fb3c92_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="460" data-rawheight="215" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="460" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-aa1478e3bb2abddb9ac6b62cc3fb3c92_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='460'%20height='215'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="460" data-rawheight="215" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="460" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-aa1478e3bb2abddb9ac6b62cc3fb3c92_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-aa1478e3bb2abddb9ac6b62cc3fb3c92_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-d2433709eb4630a44aee5995f1507f18_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="920" data-rawheight="518" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="920" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-d2433709eb4630a44aee5995f1507f18_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='920'%20height='518'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="920" data-rawheight="518" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="920" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-d2433709eb4630a44aee5995f1507f18_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-d2433709eb4630a44aee5995f1507f18_b.jpg"></figure><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-e3289c08662152ac7950b18b7e43c55f_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="1919" data-rawheight="1080" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1919" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-e3289c08662152ac7950b18b7e43c55f_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1919'%20height='1080'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="1919" data-rawheight="1080" data-caption="" data-size="normal" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="1919" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-e3289c08662152ac7950b18b7e43c55f_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-e3289c08662152ac7950b18b7e43c55f_b.jpg"></figure><p>（部分图片来自百度，侵删）</p><p><br></p><p><b>最后，码字不易，希望各位点个赞犒劳一下。</b></p><