pyable&quot;:true,&quot;isNormal&quot;:true,&quot;voteupCount&quot;:223,&quot;commentCount&quot;:28,&quot;isSticky&quot;:false,&quot;adminClosedComment&quot;:false,&quot;commentPermission&quot;:&quot;all&quot;,&quot;canComment&quot;:{&quot;reason&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;status&quot;:true},&quot;reshipmentSettings&quot;:&quot;allowed&quot;,&quot;content&quot;:&quot;【多图预警】&lt;br&gt;把游戏英文名补上了，方便知友到AppStore搜索。&lt;br&gt;推荐一些只有iOS的好玩且耐玩游戏，安卓的朋友不好意思啦。&lt;br&gt;这些游戏在AppStore上蛮贵的，但我都买了哈哈哈。&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;1.堡垒（Bastion）&lt;br&gt;《堡垒》是款角色扮演游戏；讲述大灾难将世界分割成若干漂浮岛屿，救世主KID肩负重建世界的重任。欧洲童话风格，40多张精美手绘场景，每座岛屿风格迥异，配上激情洋溢的电子乐简直完美。十余种特色鲜明的武器玩法多样，操作简单便捷，战斗畅快淋漓。&lt;br&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;noscript&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/3224364ca04a66bb90e3435c8f601ffb_b.png\&quot; data-rawwidth=\&quot;1334\&quot; data-rawheight=\&quot;750\&quot; class=\&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\&quot; width=\&quot;1334\&quot; data-original=\&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/3224364ca04a66bb90e3435c8f601ffb_r.jpg\&quot;&gt;&lt;/noscript&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&amp;lt;svg%20xmlns=&#x27;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#x27;%20width=&#x27;1334&#x27;%20height=&#x27;750&#x27;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/svg&amp;gt;\&quot; data-rawwidth=\&quot;1334\&quot; data-rawheight=\&quot;750\&quot; class=\&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\&quot; width=\&quot;1334\&quot; data-original=\&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/3224364ca04a66bb90e3435c8f601ffb_r.jpg\&quot; data-actualsrc=\&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/3224364ca04a66bb90e3435c8f601ffb_b.png\&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;noscript&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/abf686d83c2af5a666959ed08bfd8696_b.png\&quot; data-rawwidth=\&quot;1334\&quot; data-rawheight=\&quot;750\&quot; class=\&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\&quot; width=\&quot;1334\&quot; data-original=\&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/abf686d83c2af5a666959ed08bfd8696_r.jpg\&quot;&gt;&lt;/noscript&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&amp;lt;svg%20xmlns=&#x27;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#x27;%20width=&#x27;1334&#x27;%20height=&#x27;750&#x27;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/svg&amp;gt;\&quot; data-rawwidth=\&quot;1334\&quot; data-rawheight=\&quot;750\&quot; class=\&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\&quot; width=\&quot;1334\&quot; data-original=\&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/abf686d83c2af5a666959ed08bfd8696_r.jpg\&quot; data-actualsrc=\&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/abf686d83c2af5a666959ed08bfd8696_b.png\&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;noscript&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/30e4c247321943e7a2e4dad662491a64_b.png\&quot; data-rawwidth=\&quot;1334\&quot; data-rawheight=\&quot;750\&quot; class=\&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\&quot; width=\&quot;1334\&quot; data-original=\&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/30e4c247321943e7a2e4dad662491a64_r.jpg\&quot;&gt;&lt;/noscript&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&amp;lt;svg%20xmlns=&#x27;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#x27;%20width=&#x27;1334&#x27;%20height=&#x27;750&#x27;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/svg&amp;gt;\&quot; data-rawwidth=\&quot;1334\&quot; data-rawheight=\&quot;750\&quot; class=\&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\&quot; width=\&quot;1334\&quot; data-original=\&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/30e4c247321943e7a2e4dad662491a64_r.jpg\&quot; data-actualsrc=\&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/30e4c247321943e7a2e4dad662491a64_b.png\&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;2.晶体管（Transistor）&lt;br&gt;《晶体管》是款角色扮演游戏；讲述歌星RED被神秘组织袭击导致失去声音后，毅然拔出晶体管冒险解开背后谜团。赛博朋克风格题材，以计算机或信息技术为主题。画面惊艳、音效出众，完全是一场听觉与视觉盛宴。打破常规战斗模式，强调技能叠加算法，战斗效果炫酷。&lt;br&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;noscript&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/c05182a343a0c29c0fafdc08e9f78e62_b.jpg\&quot; data-rawwidth=\&quot;1280\&quot; data-rawheight=\&quot;719\&quot; class=\&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\&quot; width=\&quot;1280\&quot; data-original=\&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/c05182a343a0c29c0fafdc08e9f78e62_r.jpg\&quot;&gt;&lt;/noscript&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&amp;lt;svg%20xmlns=&#x27;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#x27;%20width=&#x27;1280&#x27;%20height=&#x27;719&#x27;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/svg&amp;gt;\&quot; data-rawwidth=\&quot;1280\&quot; data-rawheight=\&quot;719\&quot; class=\&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\&quot; width=\&quot;1280\&quot; data-original=\&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/c05182a343a0c29c0fafdc08e9f78e62_r.jpg\&quot; data-actualsrc=\&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/c05182a343a0c29c0fafdc08e9f78e62_b.jpg\&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;noscript&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/9f9e2daaaaf63f7a95cdeae1f1d3bf12_b.jpg\&quot; data-rawwidth=\&quot;1280\&quot; data-rawheight=\&quot;719\&quot; class=\&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\&quot; width=\&quot;1280\&quot; data-original=\&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/9f9e2daaaaf63f7a95cdeae1f1d3bf12_r.jpg\&quot;&gt;&lt;/noscript&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&amp;lt;svg%20xmlns=&#x27;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#x27;%20width=&#x27;1280&#x27;%20height=&#x27;719&#x27;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/svg&amp;gt;\&quot; data-rawwidth=\&quot;1280\&quot; data-rawheight=\&quot;719\&quot; class=\&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\&quot; width=\&quot;1280\&quot; data-original=\&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/9f9e2daaaaf63f7a95cdeae1f1d3bf12_r.jpg\&quot; data-actualsrc=\&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/9f9e2daaaaf63f7a95cdeae1f1d3bf12_b.jpg\&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;noscript&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/754007d5982f9b667113330b3634b735_b.jpg\&quot; data-rawwidth=\&quot;1280\&quot; data-rawheight=\&quot;719\&quot; class=\&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\&quot; width=\&quot;1280\&quot; data-original=\&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/754007d5982f9b667113330b3634b735_r.jpg\&quot;&gt;&lt;/noscript&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&amp;lt;svg%20xmlns=&#x27;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#x27;%20width=&#x27;1280&#x27;%20height=&#x27;719&#x27;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/svg&amp;gt;\&quot; data-rawwidth=\&quot;1280\&quot; data-rawheight=\&quot;719\&quot; class=\&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\&quot; width=\&quot;1280\&quot; data-original=\&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/754007d5982f9b667113330b3634b735_r.jpg\&quot; data-actualsrc=\&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/754007d5982f9b667113330b3634b735_b.jpg\&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;3.失落的记忆（Forgotten Memories：Alternate Realities）&lt;br&gt;《失落的记忆》是款恐怖解谜游戏；女主Rose在寻找失踪女孩时误入废弃庇护所，无辜中枪醒来发现身处阴森恐怖的房间。环境阴暗无比而且大部分视野需要通过手电筒照明，时不时冒出模特人偶攻击，配上丧心病狂的音乐，分分钟吓破胆。&lt;br&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;noscript&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/4bc2a124e437fc0b24cdded2e0310177_b.jpg\&quot; data-rawwidth=\&quot;640\&quot; data-rawheight=\&quot;360\&quot; class=\&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\&quot; width=\&quot;640\&quot; data-original=\&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/4bc2a124e437fc0b24cdded2e0310177_r.jpg\&quot;&gt;&lt;/noscript&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&amp;lt;svg%20xmlns=&#x27;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#x27;%20width=&#x27;640&#x27;%20height=&#x27;360&#x27;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/svg&amp;gt;\&quot; data-rawwidth=\&quot;640\&quot; data-rawheight=\&quot;360\&quot; class=\&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\&quot; width=\&quot;640\&quot; data-original=\&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/4bc2a124e437fc0b24cdded2e0310177_r.jpg\&quot; data-actualsrc=\&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/4bc2a124e437fc0b24cdded2e0310177_b.jpg\&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;noscript&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/cefb92082f5002b84675b1887ade308d_b.png\&quot; data-rawwidth=\&quot;1334\&quot; data-rawheight=\&quot;750\&quot; class=\&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\&quot; width=\&quot;1334\&quot; data-original=\&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/cefb92082f5002b84675b1887ade308d_r.jpg\&quot;&gt;&lt;/noscript&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&amp;lt;svg%20xmlns=&#x27;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#x27;%20width=&#x27;1334&#x27;%20height=&#x27;750&#x27;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/svg&amp;gt;\&quot; data-rawwidth=\&quot;1334\&quot; data-rawheight=\&quot;750\&quot; class=\&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\&quot; width=\&quot;1334\&quot; data-original=\&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/cefb92082f5002b84675b1887ade308d_r.jpg\&quot; data-actualsrc=\&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/cefb92082f5002b84675b1887ade308d_b.png\&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;noscript&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/e0f5d5e72f53af80ebe8c558de40d0d0_b.jpg\&quot; data-rawwidth=\&quot;580\&quot; data-rawheight=\&quot;326\&quot; class=\&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\&quot; width=\&quot;580\&quot; data-original=\&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/e0f5d5e72f53af80ebe8c558de40d0d0_r.jpg\&quot;&gt;&lt;/noscript&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&amp;lt;svg%20xmlns=&#x27;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#x27;%20width=&#x27;580&#x27;%20height=&#x27;326&#x27;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/svg&amp;gt;\&quot; data-rawwidth=\&quot;580\&quot; data-rawheight=\&quot;326\&quot; class=\&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\&quot; width=\&quot;580\&quot; data-original=\&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/e0f5d5e72f53af80ebe8c558de40d0d0_r.jpg\&quot; data-actualsrc=\&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/e0f5d5e72f53af80ebe8c558de40d0d0_b.jpg\&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;4.投影寻真（shadowmatic）&lt;br&gt;《投影寻真》是款影子解谜游戏；2015年度最佳iPhone游戏。设计原理类似我们中国的皮影戏，通过旋转、拼凑使看上去毫无关联的零部件，被光线投射后影子形成特定的影像。强大的物理引擎配上超仿真画面，称得上一场视觉盛宴。&lt;br&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;noscript&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/270a6826e525df4c86955f470bc505fe_b.jpg\&quot; data-rawwidth=\&quot;1136\&quot; data-rawheight=\&quot;640\&quot; class=\&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\&quot; width=\&quot;1136\&quot; data-original=\&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/270a6826e525df4c86955f470bc505fe_r.jpg\&quot;&gt;&lt;/noscript&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&amp;lt;svg%20xmlns=&#x27;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#x27;%20width=&#x27;1136&#x27;%20height=&#x27;640&#x27;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/svg&amp;gt;\&quot; data-rawwidth=\&quot;1136\&quot; data-rawheight=\&quot;640\&quot; class=\&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\&quot; width=\&quot;1136\&quot; data-original=\&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/270a6826e525df4c86955f470bc505fe_r.jpg\&quot; data-actualsrc=\&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/270a6826e525df4c86955f470bc505fe_b.jpg\&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;noscript&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/ba7b6756c549dc2d230f81e42ab2fede_b.jpg\&quot; data-rawwidth=\&quot;1136\&quot; data-rawheight=\&quot;640\&quot; class=\&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\&quot; width=\&quot;1136\&quot; data-original=\&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/ba7b6756c549dc2d230f81e42ab2fede_r.jpg\&quot;&gt;&lt;/noscript&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&amp;lt;svg%20xmlns=&#x27;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#x27;%20width=&#x27;1136&#x27;%20height=&#x27;640&#x27;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/svg&amp;gt;\&quot; data-rawwidth=\&quot;1136\&quot; data-rawheight=\&quot;640\&quot; class=\&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\&quot; width=\&quot;1136\&quot; data-original=\&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/ba7b6756c549dc2d230f81e42ab2fede_r.jpg\&quot; data-actualsrc=\&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/ba7b6756c549dc2d230f81e42ab2fede_b.jpg\&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;noscript&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/109fb7a2d8000f9b568054856e0b4e61_b.jpg\&quot; data-rawwidth=\&quot;1136\&quot; data-rawheight=\&quot;640\&quot; class=\&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\&quot; width=\&quot;1136\&quot; data-original=\&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/109fb7a2d8000f9b568054856e0b4e61_r.jpg\&quot;&gt;&lt;/noscript&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&amp;lt;svg%20xmlns=&#x27;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#x27;%20width=&#x27;1136&#x27;%20height=&#x27;640&#x27;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/svg&amp;gt;\&quot; data-rawwidth=\&quot;1136\&quot; data-rawheight=\&quot;640\&quot; class=\&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\&quot; width=\&quot;1136\&quot; data-original=\&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/109fb7a2d8000f9b568054856e0b4e61_r.jpg\&quot; data-actualsrc=\&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/109fb7a2d8000f9b568054856e0b4e61_b.jpg\&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;5.漫漫旅途（Year Walk）&lt;br&gt;《漫漫旅途》是款恐怖解谜游戏；游戏一开始就被猝不及防地就丢到地上，四周传来空灵的风声，安静得能听到自己的脚步声。没有任何指引，完全靠自己摸索。寻找的过程是种煎熬，或许下一次划动的画面会让你尖叫出来，你敢直面内心的恐惧么？&lt;br&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;noscript&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/1da536533badf67dc9c0cc9d4b0890c5_b.png\&quot; data-rawwidth=\&quot;1334\&quot; data-rawheight=\&quot;750\&quot; class=\&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\&quot; width=\&quot;1334\&quot; data-original=\&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/1da536533badf67dc9c0cc9d4b0890c5_r.jpg\&quot;&gt;&lt;/noscript&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&amp;lt;svg%20xmlns=&#x27;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#x27;%20width=&#x27;1334&#x27;%20height=&#x27;750&#x27;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/svg&amp;gt;\&quot; data-rawwidth=\&quot;1334\&quot; data-rawheight=\&quot;750\&quot; class=\&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\&quot; width=\&quot;1334\&quot; data-original=\&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/1da536533badf67dc9c0cc9d4b0890c5_r.jpg\&quot; data-actualsrc=\&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/1da536533badf67dc9c0cc9d4b0890c5_b.png\&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;noscript&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/983a6a576231754c691ebe5b7f50ed1c_b.png\&quot; data-rawwidth=\&quot;1334\&quot; data-rawheight=\&quot;750\&quot; class=\&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\&quot; width=\&quot;1334\&quot; data-original=\&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/983a6a576231754c691ebe5b7f50ed1c_r.jpg\&quot;&gt;&lt;/noscript&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&amp;lt;svg%20xmlns=&#x27;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#x27;%20width=&#x27;1334&#x27;%20height=&#x27;750&#x27;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/svg&amp;gt;\&quot; data-rawwidth=\&quot;1334\&quot; data-rawheight=\&quot;750\&quot; class=\&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\&quot; width=\&quot;1334\&quot; data-original=\&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/983a6a576231754c691ebe5b7f50ed1c_r.jpg\&quot; data-actualsrc=\&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/983a6a576231754c691ebe5b7f50ed1c_b.png\&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;noscript&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/14d2ca4ec13633a7a04f8245d2e0b7b9_b.png\&quot; data-rawwidth=\&quot;1334\&quot; data-rawheight=\&quot;750\&quot; class=\&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\&quot; width=\&quot;1334\&quot; data-original=\&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/14d2ca4ec13633a7a04f8245d2e0b7b9_r.jpg\&quot;&gt;&lt;/noscript&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&amp;lt;svg%20xmlns=&#x27;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#x27;%20width=&#x27;1334&#x27;%20height=&#x27;750&#x27;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/svg&amp;gt;\&quot; data-rawwidth=\&quot;1334\&quot; data-rawheight=\&quot;750\&quot; class=\&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\&quot; width=\&quot;1334\&quot; data-original=\&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/14d2ca4ec13633a7a04f8245d2e0b7b9_r.jpg\&quot; data-actualsrc=\&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/14d2ca4ec13633a7a04f8245d2e0b7b9_b.png\&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;6.海之号角（Oceanhorn）&lt;br&gt;《海之号角》是款角色扮演游戏；海怪重新出现，世界再次陷入黑暗，主角意外踏上充满冒险的航海之旅。背负着伟大使命的主角穿梭于一个个岛屿之间，与怪物艰苦搏斗，最终拯救世界。&lt;br&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;noscript&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/389f99768b210fc7fc205efc7eac96e6_b.jpg\&quot; data-rawwidth=\&quot;1136\&quot; data-rawheight=\&quot;640\&quot; class=\&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\&quot; width=\&quot;1136\&quot; data-original=\&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/389f99768b210fc7fc205efc7eac96e6_r.jpg\&quot;&gt;&lt;/noscript&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&amp;lt;svg%20xmlns=&#x27;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#x27;%20width=&#x27;1136&#x27;%20height=&#x27;640&#x27;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/svg&amp;gt;\&quot; data-rawwidth=\&quot;1136\&quot; data-rawheight=\&quot;640\&quot; class=\&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\&quot; width=\&quot;1136\&quot; data-original=\&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/389f99768b210fc7fc205efc7eac96e6_r.jpg\&quot; data-actualsrc=\&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/389f99768b210fc7fc205efc7eac96e6_b.jpg\&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;noscript&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/5272c7ed48879b827c9515187f503cf7_b.jpg\&quot; data-rawwidth=\&quot;1136\&quot; data-rawheight=\&quot;640\&quot; class=\&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\&quot; width=\&quot;1136\&quot; data-original=\&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/5272c7ed48879b827c9515187f503cf7_r.jpg\&quot;&gt;&lt;/noscript&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&amp;lt;svg%20xmlns=&#x27;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#x27;%20width=&#x27;1136&#x27;%20height=&#x27;640&#x27;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/svg&amp;gt;\&quot; data-rawwidth=\&quot;1136\&quot; data-rawheight=\&quot;640\&quot; class=\&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\&quot; width=\&quot;1136\&quot; data-original=\&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/5272c7ed48879b827c9515187f503cf7_r.jpg\&quot; data-actualsrc=\&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/5272c7ed48879b827c9515187f503cf7_b.jpg\&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;noscript&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/285e5d98749bef7c3f7558994db8ed7a_b.jpg\&quot; data-rawwidth=\&quot;1136\&quot; data-rawheight=\&quot;640\&quot; class=\&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\&quot; width=\&quot;1136\&quot; data-original=\&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/285e5d98749bef7c3f7558994db8ed7a_r.jpg\&quot;&gt;&lt;/noscript&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&amp;lt;svg%20xmlns=&#x27;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#x27;%20width=&#x27;1136&#x27;%20height=&#x27;640&#x27;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/svg&amp;gt;\&quot; data-rawwidth=\&quot;1136\&quot; data-rawheight=\&quot;640\&quot; class=\&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\&quot; width=\&quot;1136\&quot; data-original=\&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/285e5d98749bef7c3f7558994db8ed7a_r.jpg\&quot; data-actualsrc=\&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/285e5d98749bef7c3f7558994db8ed7a_b.jpg\&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;7.辐射岛（Radiation Island）&lt;br&gt;《辐射岛》是典型的荒岛冒险游戏，伐树、打猎、建造该有的一项没少。3D画面精美，第一人称视角，而且游戏里还有僵尸，被追着跑可是惊险万分。荒岛非常大，环境错综复杂，能生存下来并解开辐射岛秘密相当不容易。&lt;br&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;noscript&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/415745f406ee61a7ae0ddbc1cd8f1e0b_b.png\&quot; data-rawwidth=\&quot;700\&quot; data-rawheight=\&quot;394\&quot; class=\&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\&quot; width=\&quot;700\&quot; data-original=\&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/415745f406ee61a7ae0ddbc1cd8f1e0b_r.jpg\&quot;&gt;&lt;/noscript&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&amp;lt;svg%20xmlns=&#x27;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#x27;%20width=&#x27;700&#x27;%20height=&#x27;394&#x27;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/svg&amp;gt;\&quot; data-rawwidth=\&quot;700\&quot; data-rawheight=\&quot;394\&quot; class=\&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\&quot; width=\&quot;700\&quot; data-original=\&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/415745f406ee61a7ae0ddbc1cd8f1e0b_r.jpg\&quot; data-actualsrc=\&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/415745f406ee61a7ae0ddbc1cd8f1e0b_b.png\&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;noscript&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/b1beee9361cc372245cf549472506ca1_b.png\&quot; data-rawwidth=\&quot;700\&quot; data-rawheight=\&quot;394\&quot; class=\&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\&quot; width=\&quot;700\&quot; data-original=\&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/b1beee9361cc372245cf549472506ca1_r.jpg\&quot;&gt;&lt;/noscript&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&amp;lt;svg%20xmlns=&#x27;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#x27;%20width=&#x27;700&#x27;%20height=&#x27;394&#x27;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/svg&amp;gt;\&quot; data-rawwidth=\&quot;700\&quot; data-rawheight=\&quot;394\&quot; class=\&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\&quot; width=\&quot;700\&quot; data-original=\&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/b1beee9361cc372245cf549472506ca1_r.jpg\&quot; data-actualsrc=\&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/b1beee9361cc372245cf549472506ca1_b.png\&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;noscript&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/6233c02083053036346fb1406651bc87_b.png\&quot; data-rawwidth=\&quot;700\&quot; data-rawheight=\&quot;394\&quot; class=\&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\&quot; width=\&quot;700\&quot; data-original=\&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/6233c02083053036346fb1406651bc87_r.jpg\&quot;&gt;&lt;/noscript&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&amp;lt;svg%20xmlns=&#x27;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#x27;%20width=&#x27;700&#x27;%20height=&#x27;394&#x27;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/svg&amp;gt;\&quot; data-rawwidth=\&quot;700\&quot; data-rawheight=\&quot;394\&quot; class=\&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\&quot; width=\&quot;700\&quot; data-original=\&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/6233c02083053036346fb1406651bc87_r.jpg\&quot; data-actualsrc=\&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/6233c02083053036346fb1406651bc87_b.png\&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;8.英雄徽章（Hero Emblems）&lt;br&gt;《英雄徽章》是款三消RPG游戏；2015年度精选iPhone游戏。日式画风，Q萌角色，逗比的人物设定和有趣的剧情，每一点都做得十分精致。至于三消玩法，模仿日本最火爆的三消游戏《智龙迷城》，装备系统、技能系统、属性系统等角色扮演元素都运用的恰到好处。&lt;br&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;noscript&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/f5910e0b43b5dfbc30595fb6328cab10_b.jpg\&quot; data-rawwidth=\&quot;1276\&quot; data-rawheight=\&quot;1136\&quot; class=\&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\&quot; width=\&quot;1276\&quot; data-original=\&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/f5910e0b43b5dfbc30595fb6328cab10_r.jpg\&quot;&gt;&lt;/noscript&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&amp;lt;svg%20xmlns=&#x27;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#x27;%20width=&#x27;1276&#x27;%20height=&#x27;1136&#x27;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/svg&amp;gt;\&quot; data-rawwidth=\&quot;1276\&quot; data-rawheight=\&quot;1136\&quot; class=\&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\&quot; width=\&quot;1276\&quot; data-original=\&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/f5910e0b43b5dfbc30595fb6328cab10_r.jpg\&quot; data-actualsrc=\&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/f5910e0b43b5dfbc30595fb6328cab10_b.jpg\&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;noscript&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/4dc72cd723b3099f8facdf0f7cf2f575_b.jpg\&quot; data-rawwidth=\&quot;1276\&quot; data-rawheight=\&quot;1136\&quot; class=\&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\&quot; width=\&quot;1276\&quot; data-original=\&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/4dc72cd723b3099f8facdf0f7cf2f575_r.jpg\&quot;&gt;&lt;/noscript&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&amp;lt;svg%20xmlns=&#x27;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#x27;%20width=&#x27;1276&#x27;%20height=&#x27;1136&#x27;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/svg&amp;gt;\&quot; data-rawwidth=\&quot;1276\&quot; data-rawheight=\&quot;1136\&quot; class=\&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\&quot; width=\&quot;1276\&quot; data-original=\&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/4dc72cd723b3099f8facdf0f7cf2f575_r.jpg\&quot; data-actualsrc=\&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/4dc72cd723b3099f8facdf0f7cf2f575_b.jpg\&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;noscript&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/89b335cbb32ee2462d8c6ba32d57cddb_b.jpg\&quot; data-rawwidth=\&quot;1276\&quot; data-rawheight=\&quot;1136\&quot; class=\&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\&quot; width=\&quot;1276\&quot; data-original=\&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/89b335cbb32ee2462d8c6ba32d57cddb_r.jpg\&quot;&gt;&lt;/noscript&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&amp;lt;svg%20xmlns=&#x27;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#x27;%20width=&#x27;1276&#x27;%20height=&#x27;1136&#x27;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/svg&amp;gt;\&quot; data-rawwidth=\&quot;1276\&quot; data-rawheight=\&quot;1136\&quot; class=\&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\&quot; width=\&quot;1276\&quot; data-original=\&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/89b335cbb32ee2462d8c6ba32d57cddb_r.jpg\&quot; data-actualsrc=\&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/89b335cbb32ee2462d8c6ba32d57cddb_b.jpg\&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;9.AG飞车（AG Drive）&lt;br&gt;《AG飞车》是款竞速游戏；赛道不再是蜿蜒曲折的小道或繁华热闹的都市道路，而是盘绕在城市上空的飞车轨道，未来世界的城市或许就长这样，科幻感十足的城市震撼双眼，加上有趣的跑道设计，每一次加速都让人热血澎湃~&lt;br&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;noscript&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/a58cb58ed22272c55315a2266d251c13_b.jpg\&quot; data-rawwidth=\&quot;1280\&quot; data-rawheight=\&quot;719\&quot; class=\&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\&quot; width=\&quot;1280\&quot; data-original=\&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/a58cb58ed22272c55315a2266d251c13_r.jpg\&quot;&gt;&lt;/noscript&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&amp;lt;svg%20xmlns=&#x27;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#x27;%20width=&#x27;1280&#x27;%20height=&#x27;719&#x27;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/svg&amp;gt;\&quot; data-rawwidth=\&quot;1280\&quot; data-rawheight=\&quot;719\&quot; class=\&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\&quot; width=\&quot;1280\&quot; data-original=\&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/a58cb58ed22272c55315a2266d251c13_r.jpg\&quot; data-actualsrc=\&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/a58cb58ed22272c55315a2266d251c13_b.jpg\&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;noscript&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/d4960a6d39c16f881659ea42835db324_b.jpg\&quot; data-rawwidth=\&quot;1280\&quot; data-rawheight=\&quot;719\&quot; class=\&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\&quot; width=\&quot;1280\&quot; data-original=\&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/d4960a6d39c16f881659ea42835db324_r.jpg\&quot;&gt;&lt;/noscript&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&amp;lt;svg%20xmlns=&#x27;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#x27;%20width=&#x27;1280&#x27;%20height=&#x27;719&#x27;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/svg&amp;gt;\&quot; data-rawwidth=\&quot;1280\&quot; data-rawheight=\&quot;719\&quot; class=\&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\&quot; width=\&quot;1280\&quot; data-original=\&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/d4960a6d39c16f881659ea42835db324_r.jpg\&quot; data-actualsrc=\&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/d4960a6d39c16f881659ea42835db324_b.jpg\&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;noscript&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/cfe1691b37240c47b1d6f79d36d8dbc5_b.jpg\&quot; data-rawwidth=\&quot;1280\&quot; data-rawheight=\&quot;719\&quot; class=\&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\&quot; width=\&quot;1280\&quot; data-original=\&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/cfe1691b37240c47b1d6f79d36d8dbc5_r.jpg\&quot;&gt;&lt;/noscript&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&amp;lt;svg%20xmlns=&#x27;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#x27;%20width=&#x27;1280&#x27;%20height=&#x27;719&#x27;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/svg&amp;gt;\&quot; data-rawwidth=\&quot;1280\&quot; data-rawheight=\&quot;719\&quot; class=\&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\&quot; width=\&quot;1280\&quot; data-original=\&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/cfe1691b37240c47b1d6f79d36d8dbc5_r.jpg\&quot; data-actualsrc=\&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/cfe1691b37240c47b1d6f79d36d8dbc5_b.jpg\&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;10.爷爷的城市（Lumino City）&lt;br&gt;《爷爷的城市》是款冒险解谜游戏；游戏中的所有场景均用&lt;strong&gt;纸模&lt;/strong&gt;手工搭建，3米高的城市在游戏工作室中真实存在。玩家需操控名为Lumi的小女孩在城市中寻找她的爷爷，顺道帮居民们解决各种鸡毛蒜皮的问题，一步步看整座城市鲜活起来~&lt;br&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;noscript&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/0d19d944feff3a6cfc6c9c8b63b4abde_b.jpg\&quot; data-rawwidth=\&quot;2048\&quot; data-rawheight=\&quot;1536\&quot; class=\&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\&quot; width=\&quot;2048\&quot; data-original=\&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/0d19d944feff3a6cfc6c9c8b63b4abde_r.jpg\&quot;&gt;&lt;/noscript&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&amp;lt;svg%20xmlns=&#x27;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#x27;%20width=&#x27;2048&#x27;%20height=&#x27;1536&#x27;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/svg&amp;gt;\&quot; data-rawwidth=\&quot;2048\&quot; data-rawheight=\&quot;1536\&quot; class=\&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\&quot; width=\&quot;2048\&quot; data-original=\&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/0d19d944feff3a6cfc6c9c8b63b4abde_r.jpg\&quot; data-actualsrc=\&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/0d19d944feff3a6cfc6c9c8b63b4abde_b.jpg\&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;noscript&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/cedb863d6acda6fe5448cb4fb25da5e4_b.jpg\&quot; data-rawwidth=\&quot;2048\&quot; data-rawheight=\&quot;1536\&quot; class=\&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\&quot; width=\&quot;2048\&quot; data-original=\&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/cedb863d6acda6fe5448cb4fb25da5e4_r.jpg\&quot;&gt;&lt;/noscript&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&amp;lt;svg%20xmlns=&#x27;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#x27;%20width=&#x27;2048&#x27;%20height=&#x27;1536&#x27;